(1, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Advanced knowledge in MVC architecture and object-oriented programming</li><li>Experience in web development with a server-side language such as PHP(Laravel, CodeIgniter, CakePHP)</li><li>Experience in jQuery, Rest API, JSON</li><li>Should have knowledge of HTML, Bootstrap and CSS</li><li>Experience in web services, Rest API, JSON, SOAP, Linux/Unix.</li><li>Professional experience of version control (Git)</li><li>Working knowledge with MYSQL databases</li><li>Experience on AWS, Heroku cloud services will be a plus</li><li>Advanced knowledge in MVC architecture and object-oriented programming</li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>3+ years\' of experience in web development and software design</li><li>Expertise in front-end technologies (HTML, JavaScript, CSS), PHP frameworks, and MySQL databases</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Mohali district, Punjab, India', 'WorksDelight', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3239967512/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=Tra7sjP5%2B8N03Om2pxkh2Q%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'WorksDelight is an IT services, consulting and business solutions organization that delivers accurate results to global business, ensuring a level of certainty that no other firm can match. We are specialized in providing the perfect UI/UX or Web Development services.\n\nAs the best web development company, we at WorksDelight, specialize in building creative, attractive, and efficient websites and apps for you.\n\nOur unique industry-based, consultative approach helps clients envision, build and run more innovative and efficient businesses. The work is delivered through our adept team of innovators across the globe, differentiated by the imagination and recognized as the benchmark of excellence in software development.The company generated consolidated revenues of US $1 million for the year ended March 31, 2016 . For more information, visit us at www.worksdelight.com.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3239967512/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=Tra7sjP5%2B8N03Om2pxkh2Q%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:17:40'),
(2, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                Responsibilities<br>\n<br>\nConducting analysis of website and application requirements.<br>\nWriting back-end code and building efficient PHP modules.<br>\nDeveloping back-end portals with an optimized database.<br>\nTroubleshooting application and code issues.<br>\nIntegrating data storage solutions.<br>\nResponding to integration requests from front-end developers.<br>\nFinalizing back-end features and testing web applications.<br>\n<br>\nKey Skills<br>\n<br>\n﻿PHP / Laravel / CodeIgniter / HTML / CSS/ MySQL/ PostgreSQL / Ajax Javascript / Bootstrap / API Integration\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India', 'Mindbox Technologies', 'Sanjay Idhatiya', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244519952/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=j%2FH3z2EWDJ7BEjPFhWdG6g%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Mindbox Technologies offers a full-fledged set of IT services through the well-versed knowledge and experience we\'ve assembled in the last 10+ years. Designs have utilized the master in WordPress, Magento, Joomla, CodeIgniter, CakePHP, PHP, Laravel, and Website Designing to give you the best administration in this area.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244519952/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=j%2FH3z2EWDJ7BEjPFhWdG6g%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:17:45'),
(3, 'HTML Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p>We are looking for an experienced HTML developer to oversee the design, coding, and implementation of website projects for our clients. In this role, you will be required to collaborate with Website Designers on the initial web design, write the code, ensure cross-platform compatibility, and provide user support.</p><p>To be successful as an HTML developer, you should have a good eye for detail and excellent knowledge of front-end technologies. Ultimately a top-notch HTML developer should be proficient in web design, a master coder, and someone with the skills to provide user support.</p><p><br>\n</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>HTML Developer Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Meeting with Web designers to discuss project design and layout.</li><li>Coding the entire HTML site from end to end.</li><li>Debugging code and front-end web applications.</li><li>Ensuring cross-platform compatibility.</li><li>Troubleshooting application errors.</li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>HTML Developer Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>In-depth knowledge of front-end coding languages including HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and XML.</li><li>Ability to troubleshoot coding and application errors.</li></ul><p></p>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Rajkot, Gujarat, India', 'Ace Infoway Pvt. Ltd.', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3239997010/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=ihk%2FQTLJ6F5sqh5f8OnNdA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Ace Infoway is a passionate ‘go-to’ Technology Partner for web/software agencies and businesses in various industry verticals, across the globe as an extended partner and offshore development center.\nWith a tech-focused vision, we ensure to create success stories for their clients above all else