(16, 'apply for the Full Stack Developer-Full Time', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember71\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                About the Product: PBIVizEdit is a powerful SaaS product that targets the high growth BI Analytics market. We already of boast of users (including free and paid) across 3000 companies worldwide with enterprises like Microsoft, Amazon, Intel, Deloitte, BMW using our product. The Full-Stack developers will work with our Co-Founder to develop new features and maintain the current ones. As the initial joinees this is an opportunity with high growth potential and possibly good financial benefits if and when we make an exit. Roles and Responsibilities: We need a Full Stack Developer who is proficient in MERN stack. The applicant MUST be: *Proficient with web technology stack (HTML5, CSS, JavaScript, etc.) *Able to understand and write REST web services. *Able to understand software design, architecture and design constraints. *Able to do manual testing (like unit testing, system testing, etc.) NICE to have: *Experience in the pre-processors like Typescript and SASS/SCSS. *Able to write clean and easy to understand single page applications in React. *Can author REST web services in express/NodeJS with MongoDB as backend. *Should be able to provision, deploy and monitor services on AWS instances with/without containerization. *Understanding of various javascript charting libraries like Plotly, etc. *Experience in general software engineering processes, like SCRUM. *Able to gather software requirements from various stake holders, analyze them and propose solutions. *If you read this line, drop an email to \'recruit@yavda.in\' with subject line - pbivizedit mern *Attention to detail is important for us. *Able to understand different application testing paradigms (like unit testing, system testing, etc.) and write tests in automated way. *Experience in data visualization (charts/graphs concepts in Plotly, Power BI, Tableau or related tools). Perks and Benefits: * Enjoy the perks of working with a nimble, fast growing company. We grow. Together. *Potential for higher financial payout during Exit *Excellent learning. You will be working with our co-founder with 18 years development experience. Boost your career with fast growing company *22 days paid vacations with 10 holidays *If you hate office politics, you would love it here. As a small company, you report to a co-founder. You deliver, you succeed. Simple. *Excellent Pay *Mentoring *Group Health Insurance Selection Process: Our process has 3 steps 1. Basic online assessment - You will get a short 1 hr test link that you will need to register and take the test. This test is with Webcam so you need to have access to a laptop/desktop computer with webcam. 2. Technical assessment (online) 3. Interview with a co-founder<p><br>\n</p><strong><u>Experience</u></strong><p><br>\n</p>1-2yrs<p><br>\n</p><strong><u>Skills</u></strong><p><br>\n</p>HTML,Javascript,CSS<p><br>\n</p>Apply Now<p><br>\n</p>,<p><br>\n</p>This job is provided by Shine.com\n            <br>\n            <h3 class=\"js-skills-header t-16 t-black--light t-bold\">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n            \" single page applications\", css, \" health insurance\", html, \" online assessment\", jquery, javascript, mysql\n        </span>\n      ', 'Bhubaneshwar, Odisha, India', 'Her Second Innings', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245001790/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=XCnR6kXVaftAQhPcv48upw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Visit our portal at www.hersecondinnings.com to join hands with us in empowering women to become financially independent. Watch how Accenture helped our community in preparing for interview with EQ using AI enabled tool - https://youtu.be/O5OP8_JYN4A\n\nHer Second Innings has been created as a platform to make women financially independent, emotionally strong and socially empowered.\n\nHer Second Innings empowers women professionals at all levels. We assist women professionals, right from identifying their career passion through coaching , assess their career strengths, enabling them with training and skills to transition them to career track. There are ‘work from home’ options, temporary assignments, permanent jobs, projects and consultancy and entrepreneurial opportunities. Join us, as we work with you to embark on an exciting journey of self-discovery and financial freedom.\n\nRegister with us and avail the myriad benefits we have to offer, by\nExploring new opportunities\nFinding Corporate and Home-based Jobs according to a flexible schedule\nNurturing your Entrepreneurial streak\nCollaborating with Industry Experts and getting mentored by them\nSharing and accessing knowledge, expertise and success stories through our networking platform\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245001790/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=XCnR6kXVaftAQhPcv48upw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:19:36');
INSERT INTO `jobs_data` (`id`, `job_title`, `job_description`, `job_location`, `company_name`, `person_name`, `job_type`, `category`, `apply_link`, `about_the_company`, `job_url`, `status`, `is_featured`, `source`, `created_date`) VALUES
(17, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p>We are looking to hire a talented PHP developer to manage our back-end services and ensure a seamless data interchange between the server and our users. As a PHP developer, you will be responsible for developing and coding all server-side logic. You will also be required to maintain the central database and respond to requests from front-end developers.</p><p>To ensure success as a PHP developer, you should have in-depth knowledge of object-oriented PHP programming, an understanding of MVC designs, and working knowledge of front-end technologies including HTML5, JavaScript, and CSS3. Ultimately, a top-level PHP Developer can design and build efficient PHP modules while seamlessly integrating front-end technologies.</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>PHP Developer Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>- Conducting analysis of website and application requirements.</p><p>- Writing back-end code and building efficient PHP modules.</p><p>- Developing back-end portals with an optimized database.</p><p>- Troubleshooting application and code issues.</p><p>- Integrating data storage solutions.</p><p>- Responding to integration requests from front-end developers.</p><p>- Finalizing back-end features and testing web applications.</p><p>- Updating and altering application features to enhance performance.</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>PHP Developer Requirements:</strong></p><p>- Bachelor’s degree in computer science or a similar field.</p><p>- Knowledge of PHP web frameworks including <strong>Laravel, and CodeIgniter.</strong></p><p>- Knowledge of front-end technologies including CSS3, JavaScript, and HTML5.</p><p>- Understanding of object-oriented PHP programming.</p><p>- Previous experience creating scalable applications.</p><p>- Proficient with code versioning tools including Git, bitbucket, etc.</p><p>- Familiarity with SQL/NoSQL databases.</p><p>- Ability to manage projects.</p><p>- Good problem-solving skills.</p><p>Salary - 30000 - 50000</p><p>Experience - 2+ years</p><p>contract length - 1 year</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Ability to commute/relocate:</p><ul><li>Ahmedabad, Ahmedabad - 38001, Gujarat: Reliably commute or planning to relocate before starting work (Required)</li></ul><p>Education:</p><ul><li>Bachelor\'s (Required)</li></ul><p>Experience:</p><ul><li>PHP: 1 year (Required)</li><li>Codeigniter: 1 year (Required)</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India', 'codExalters', 'HR codExalters Techlabs', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244390757/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=VOctvr7JTojND7FKVXkfPw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'codExalters Techlabs was started in 2015 with an aim to create world class software solutions. In the startup days, it was working on software solutions for different agents. But, now codExalters works with wide range of companies and in different technologies. codExalters is now a full-fledged IT solution provider with providing expertise services like website designing, mobile application development, e-commerce solutions, ERP, rich web application services, Hiring Developer and much more all just at one place.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244390757/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=VOctvr7JTojND7FKVXkfPw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:19:45'),
(18, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                Role : PHP Freelance<br>\n<br>\nSalary : According to Work <br>\n<br>\n<br>\nStack: Frontend-HTML, CSS, JavaScript; Backend: PHP, Database-MySQL, CodeIgnitor MVC pattern<br>\n<br>\nResponsibility:<br>\n<br>\n1. Writing cron job for repetitive actions like sending emails to multiple clients, sending notification <br>\n2. Writing code for displaying notification in portal<br>\n3. Doing some display changes in portal <br>\n4. Writing some new functions and features in portal <br>\n5. Writing code to migrate data from EC2 to s3 bucket<br>\n<br>\n\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'India', 'Medworld Solutions Pvt Ltd', 'Akriti Kumari', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244569677/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=BdrEYEalVkxQXX7WwKvipQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244569677/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=BdrEYEalVkxQXX7WwKvipQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:19:53'),
(19, 'Web Development Training and Internship', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p>Corizo is one of the nation\'s fastest-growing EdTech platforms. We are looking for student interns who are looking to upskill themselves in the domain of Web Development.</p><p>*TRAINING FEES APPLICABLE*</p><p>USE CODE CORIZO30 FOR A 35% DISCOUNT.</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Apply Now:</p><p><br>\n</p><p>https://forms.gle/mx1C9XrBPAjoUfyr7</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Internship deliverables:</p><p>· One month of training from industry professionals</p><p>· Two live project opportunities</p><p>· Certificates for completion of training as well as internship</p><p>· Letter of Recommendation</p><p>· Placement Assistance</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Internship perks:</p><p>· Get the opportunity to learn from some of the leading experts in the field of Web Development.</p><p>· exposure to Industry grade projects</p><p>· Insight into industry requirements and standards</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Internship Duration:</p><p>· 2 months</p><p>· 1-month training + 1-month internship</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Certificates:</p><p>· Training certification</p><p>· Internship Certificate</p><p>· Letter of Recommendation</p><p>· Certificate of Excellence</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Start date:</p><p>· 5th September</p><p><br>\n</p><p>*TRAINING FEES APPLICABLE*</p><p>USE CODE CORIZO35 FOR A 35% DISCOUNT.</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Apply Now:</p><p><br>\n</p><p>https://forms.gle/mx1C9XrBPAjoUfyr7</p><p><br>\n</p><p>##ONLY FOR INTERESTED STUDENTS##</p><p>#opportunity #datascience #training #opportunities #students #edtech #project #internship #projects #internship #projects #webdevelopment #machinelearning #cybersecurity</p>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'India', 'Corizo', 'Mayank Dubey', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244580288/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=DAtEx41kSxzE%2Fd5020x%2BlQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Corizo is an edtech platform that helps students with internships, professional training programs, career guidance, and mentorship. Our aim is to bridge the gap between formal education and the ever changing requirements of the industry.\nAt Corizo, we believe everyone should have the opportunity to create progress through technology and develop the skills of tomorrow. With assessments, learning paths and courses authored by industry experts, our platform helps individuals benchmark expertise across roles. Our mission is to train the world’s workforce in the careers of the future. We partner with leading technology companies to learn how technology is transforming industries, and teach the critical tech skills that companies are looking for in their workforce.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244580288/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=DAtEx41kSxzE%2Fd5020x%2BlQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:20:02'),
(20, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p><strong>The ideal candidate is a highly resourceful and innovative developer with extensive experience in the layout, design and coding of webs &amp; Mobile Applications specifically in using PHP/Laravel programming language and MySQL Server databases.</strong> </p><p> </p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform a mix of maintenance, enhancements, and new development as required</li><li>Must have experience of web/Mobile application development using <strong>PHP Laravel/CI, Server and databases</strong></li><li>1.5+ years of experience working on Laravel/CI framework.</li><li>A solid understanding of application design using Laravel.</li><li>Experience with Git / GitHub (or equivalent version control system).</li><li>Experience with developing and consuming RESTful APIs.</li><li>Experience writing PHP unit tests.</li><li>Perform a responsibility of development, maintenance, and enhancements</li><li>Understanding of open-source projects</li><li>Understanding the fully synchronous behaviour of PHP</li><li><strong>Good to have AWS Cloud Experience/Knowledge.</strong></li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li><strong>1.6+ years\' of experience in web development and software design</strong></li><li><strong>Expertise in front-end technologies (HTML, JavaScript, CSS), PHP frameworks(Laravel/CI) and MySQL databases</strong></li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p>Thanks &amp; Regads</p><p>Shifali Gupta | HR Executive</p><p>TechGropse Pvt Ltd</p>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Uttar Pradesh, India', 'TechGropse Pvt. Ltd.', 'Shifali Gupta', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245067100/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=p5GGF6a%2FR1n8SCnCdVxg3w%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'TechGropse is one of the Top Mobile Application Development Companies in India, the US, and the UAE. We have served 100+ clients with a team of dedicated Android and iOS developers. We cater to services in various domains like taxi booking, restaurants, healthcare, retail and more.\n\nOur Expertise:\n\n#1. Android Application Development\n#2. iPhone/iOS Application Development\n#3. Wearable Application Development\n#4. Cross-Platform App Development\n#5. Website Design & Development\n#6. Xamarin App Development\n#7. Digital Marketing Services\n\nWe deploy agile methodology for Android and iOS app development offering robust and scalable app development solutions for our clients globally. Contact us to craft an outstanding application!\n\nWhy TechGropse?\n\n>Global service provider with offices in India, the UAE, and the USA.\n>100+ mobile app developers.\n>100% client satisfaction and 80+ repeated clients.\n>Core team of 100+ dedicated employees with strong expertise in multiple technical domains.\n>Deploys the latest tools, techniques, methodologies, and strategies to deliver a bug-free mobile application.\n>Agile approach and result-driven methodology.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245067100/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=p5GGF6a%2FR1n8SCnCdVxg3w%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:20:11'),
(21, 'WordPress Developer (India | m/w/x | Bangalore / Remote)', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <strong>At THISIS! DMG we are hungry for opportunities to improve the digital world.<br>\n<br>\n</strong>As a service provider our clients benefit from our unique ability to think beyond technology and design to make their business more efficient. Our client relationships are based on our shared values of respect, thinking beyond, and responsiveness. While we see ourselves as experts in the digital field, we are always learning, always challenging our thinking, and always looking for the next big step to improve businesses. That’s why we believe that the perfect candidate will challenge the status quo on a daily base while bringing exciting projects to<br>\n<br>\nlife.<br>\n<br>\nWe are hungry for more – join us if your appetite is big enough.<br>\n<br>\nAs a <strong>Wordpress Developer</strong>, you will be responsible for the Implementation of Wordpress Projects.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>Tasks<br>\n<br>\n</strong><strong>What you will do:<br>\n<br>\n</strong>Your most important task is to help your team deliver good software projects and platforms that the whole team is proud of. That can include the following tasks<br>\n<ul><li>Develop and revamp creative, eye-catching websites as per the client needs.</li><li>Work with project managers to discuss the desired website functionality and provide solutions.</li><li>Integrate custom templates/themes into WordPress.</li><li>Work with various WordPress third-party plugins (WooCommerce, Elementor, and others) and customize when required.</li><li>Work with third-party API integrations for eCommerce solutions (credit card payments, shipping APIs, etc.).</li><li>Design, develop and optimize websites.</li><li>Conduct website performance tests.</li><li>Maintain legacy code</li><li>Manage all technical aspects of WordPress</li><li>Manage security aspects of the WordPress</li><li>Suggest best practices, innovative ideas, and methods for attracting new and existing clients<br>\n</li></ul><strong><u>Requirements<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong><strong>What you will have:<br>\n</strong><ul><li>Excellent knowledge of WordPress Architecture, WooCommerce, Visual Composer, and other best practice solutions</li><li>Excellent knowledge of PHP, MySQL</li><li>Good knowledge HTML/HTML5/XHTML, XML, AJAX, JavaScript/jQuery, CSS/CSS3</li><li>Excellent knowledge of child theme creation and customization as per designed mockup based on the requirements</li><li>Excellent knowledge of WordPress plugin and backend development</li><li>Strong sense of visual design</li><li>An understanding of front-end optimization techniques</li><li>Excellent knowledge of website speed optimization</li><li>Knowledge of usability/user experience design is a plus<br>\n</li></ul><strong><u>Benefits<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong><strong>Career &amp; Continuing Education<br>\n</strong><ul><li>Benefiting from success together: For compensation, we follow the principle of good pay for good performance. Our maxim is: Profit from success together. That\'s why performance-based compensation systems play a crucial role for us - even outside the upper management levels.</li><li>We support your further development: For on-the-job learning, we offer the DMG Academy, a mentoring program and advanced internal training.</li><li>Step by step to the top: Regular evaluation and employee appraisals<br>\n</li></ul><strong>Individualized<br>\n</strong><ul><li>Individualized working hours and working time models: You are free to choose when you work, around the 2 hour core hours. We offer part-time and full-time positions as well as flexible changes in between.</li><li>Individualized work locations: We support you in freely choosing your work location - you decide from where you work with us, worldwide.</li><li>Individualized benefits: Extended health insurance, also worldwide - support for private pension plans.</li><li>Individualized support for home/remote office<br>\n</li></ul><strong>What we do?<br>\n</strong><ul><li>The next big thing: We are doing today what customers will see as innovative tomorrow. Topics like NFTs, Sound Interfaces, LoRa, Metaverse and Metahuman are currently topics we are working on.</li><li>Our Groundwork: We implement the full range of digital projects for our clients - from CMS, PWAs and mobile apps to 3D animations and deployment structures.</li><li>Our style: We work on projects worldwide with teams of over 15 nationalities, our working language is English, we work on topics that move our clients forward and our people are good at finding the most efficient solution.<br>\n</li></ul><strong>No matter who you are, where you come from, what you believe, or what you geek out about, we bring people together to make great work. That\'s what makes us THIS IS! Digital Media Group.<br>\n<br>\n</strong>If you love development, you should join us!\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Bengaluru, Karnataka, India', 'THIS IS! Digital Media Group', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245934019/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=qsN8GcgNj%2BFn%2BR2khpdL0w%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'We develop digital experiences. We take pride in solving digital challenges not only with our current tech stack but also with emerging innovations. This discovery drives us and keeps us curious every day.', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245934019/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=qsN8GcgNj%2BFn%2BR2khpdL0w%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:20:19'),
(22, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember74\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                Strong knowledge of any PHP web frameworks such as codeigniter, Laravel, Yii, etc<p><br>\n</p>Strong knowledge of Core PHP<p><br>\n</p>Understanding of MVC design patterns<p><br>\n</p>such as JavaScript/Jquery, HTML5, and CSS3<p><br>\n</p>Good knowledge of oops concept, Mysql<p><br>\n</p>Salary 4 Lac To 7 Lac P.A. Industry IT Software - Application Programming / Maintenance Work Experience 2 - 8 Years Qualification Other Bachelor Degree<p><br>\n</p>,<p><br>\n</p>This job is provided by Shine.com\n            <br>\n            <h3 class=\"js-skills-header t-16 t-black--light t-bold\">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n            \" application programming\", oops, html5, html, yii, php, it, software, design, javascript, laravel, css, mysql, jquery, codeigniter\n        </span>\n      ', 'New Delhi, Delhi, India', 'Capital Placement Services Gurgaon .', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245025244/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=njTKxCUtprWm1UycaS2%2B%2Bw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Capital Placement Services Gurgaon is an emerging leader in Executive Search. Capital Placement Services Gurgaon is building a tradition of providing professional, personalized, high quality services, tailor made to suit your individual needs and requirements. We have experience in both IT and non-IT Sectors such as FMCG, Retail, Telecom, Manufacturing, HealthCare, Banking, Insurance, Financial Services, and Research among others. Our forte is in identifying talent for Senior Management positions as well as Middle Management levels.\n\nWe undertake placements for both Domestic and International clients, and have ongoing engagements with several large MNC\'s within India and abroad. We operate through domain-specialist teams spread across the country, providing high quality permanent staffing services .Our success is our ability to connect the right people to the best Companies.\n\nWe are a well established and professionally managed Manpower Placement Consultants specializing in placement of managerial personnel across a wide spectrum of skills and functions. We have been in the industry for a decade and have been providing quality service to our clients across various industries. Our role begins with the client\'s need and we go to great lengths to understand the nature and complexity of the client\'s business. It is this power that helps us to provide our clients with candidates who are of the right profile.\n\n\nWe have huge data bank of candidates in all fields at all levels.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245025244/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=9h9Ykep%2FmonNFhWqngWT7A%3D%3D&trackingId=njTKxCUtprWm1UycaS2%2B%2Bw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:20:27'),
