    </span>\n      ', 'Kochi, Kerala, India', 'Axon International Coaching and Consulting', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245000882/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=4m0NEqf9glGc6EMw6z9XEw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'AICC is a startup initiative for coaching and consulting firm that believes in the power of the human capital. We believe that everyone has the capability to do wonders and achieve excellence they only need the right direction and guidance. We at AICC are always ready to nurture people and help them grow. The investment in human and intellectual capital is the best investment that is bound to deliver returns irrespective of the market conditions.\n\nAICC was started in 2021 with a vision to provide solutions to all areas of human resource development under one roof to our clients. It is a task to have separate consultants for various areas like Life Coaching , Business Coaching, Career Development and Sales Training, Staffing, SEO, Content Writing, Skill Development, Recruitment, Training\'s, Management Advisory, Employee Satisfaction Surveys, etc.\n\nWe serves both large and small organizations across all industry sectors through our brands and offerings: Coaching and Talent solutions.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245000882/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=4m0NEqf9glGc6EMw6z9XEw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:21:23'),
(24, 'Full Stack Developer Intern', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p>About DataToBiz -</p><p>DataToBiz is an AI and Big Data Analytics company, trying to solve some very exciting</p><p>business challenges by applying cutting-edge technologies and coming up with innovative</p><p>data solutions. We are a team of young and dynamic professionals.</p><p>Experience – Min 2 years.</p><p>Required Experience, Skills and Qualifications:</p><p><br>\n</p><p>- Front End Skills - HTML,CSS,Javascript (Must), ReactJs, Angular</p><p>- Back End Skills - Python (Good to have)</p><p>- Database - MySQL (Must), MongoDB/PostgreSQL (Good to have)</p><p>- Operating System - Linux</p><p>- Versioning System - Git</p><p><br>\n</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Responsibilities and Duties:</p><p><br>\n</p><p>● As a Full Stack Developer in our team, you will be responsible for providing</p><p>complete end to end deployment solution and applications /algorithms to cloud in the</p><p>form of web application/solution.</p><p>● One of the primary responsibilities will be to develop the custom solution including</p><p>front-end, back-end and database management.</p><p>● Hosting the application on cloud using AWS/Google Cloud or any other web</p><p>deployment platform and monitoring the servers in order to ensure zero downtime.</p><p>● Good sense of designing the UI/UX in a user friendly and creative way.</p><p>● Scaling the application in case of increased traffic and app usage</p><p>● Writing and testing new code along with ability to debug and maintain the existing</p><p>code.</p><p>● Able to transform the client’s custom requirements into coding</p>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Chandigarh, India', 'DataToBiz', 'Aastha Jain', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3239970979/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=MWLiouGA7EyMkETX274dUA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'We are an AI and Big Data Analytics firm, which helps organisations in managing their data assets, and finding the best ways to surface insights from the data to enable them with data centric decisions.\n\nOur mission is crystal clear. We deep dive into data to unlock insight and have the courage to act. Making use of data is the process we adopt with an aim to solve business problem statements. We work with our clients to build the analytics capabilities that enable organisations to achieve sustainable advantage.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3239970979/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=MWLiouGA7EyMkETX274dUA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:21:28'),
(25, 'Sr. Frontend Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p>We are looking for looking for Frontend Developer who have 0-1 years of experience designing, developing and implementing cross-browser web applications. Zelthy is a fast-growing next generation Platform-As-A-Service (PaaS) solution for creating healthcare applications, currently used by top global pharmaceutical companies.</p><p><br>\n</p><p>As a <strong>Frontend Developer,</strong> you would be required to</p><p><br>\n</p><p>• Development of new and existing features for the Zelthy Cloud Platform</p><p>• Collaborate with designers and UX experts to deliver an effective user experience</p><p>• Building reusable components and translating designs and concepts into high quality, maintainable and performant code</p><p>• Define together with the back-end engineers the REST APIs for the features of the services being built using JSON format (input and output) and implement the processing of the API related data</p><p>• Stay educated on the latest in software development methodologies and new technologies and continually works to innovate and build new web experiences</p><p>• Participate in design and code reviews</p><p>• Estimate projects, work closely with technical and business teams at each stage of the development lifecycle</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>What we are looking for</strong></p><p><br>\n</p><p>• 3-5 years of experience and strong understanding of web development fundamentals including HTML5, CSS, and JavaScript</p><p>• Bachelor\'s degree in Computer Science or related technical field or equivalent work experience. </p><p>• Understanding of software design patterns </p><p>• Proficiency in Git </p><p>• Troubleshooting and design skills</p><p>• Knowledge of package managers like yarn/npm</p><p>• Knowledge of foundational web programming principles including responsive design</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Desirable Skills</strong></p><p><br>\n</p><p>• Knowledge and experience of ReactJS and jQuery.</p><p>• Knowledge and experience in mobile application development using React-Native.</p><p>• Understanding of accessibility principles</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>At Zelthy you will get</strong></p><p><br>\n</p><p>An opportunity to be an early member of a team building a Tech Platform gaining strong global acceptance. Performance based equity and opportunity to evolve into a key leadership role within the organization. </p><p>Complete lifecycle view of client accounts from acquisition to project development and deployment. Work with a performance oriented team driven by ownership and open to experiments. Build SaaS/PaaS platform for global Pharmaceutical firms Work in Meritocracy driven, candid culture. No politics.</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Benefits &amp; Opportunities</strong></p><p><br>\n</p><p>Ours is a young team with minimal management structure. As a full-time employee of Zelthy, you will also have access to our comprehensive benefits program, which includes </p><p><br>\n</p><p>• Competitive salary </p><p>• Individual performance bonus</p><p>• Annual bonus opportunities</p><p>• ESOP plan </p><p>• Comprehensive health benefits</p><p>• Paid time off when you need it (as per the policy)</p><p>• Innovative work arrangement opportunities including remote work</p><p>• Paid paternity and maternity leaves</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>About Us</strong></p><p>Zelthy Cloud (https://www.zelthy.com/) is a Health Cloud (Platform-as-a-Service solution) that enables implementation and deployment of Health Program applications. The platform is used by global pharmaceutical companies, health-tech companies and other healthcare organizations for quickly setting up complex web and mobile applications. The platform is used Pharmaceutical/HealthCare firms such as Bristol-Meyer-Suibb, 1mg, Cipla, DKSH, Novo Nordisk, etc to provide their services to more than 1 million patients in 12 countries. </p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Key applications powered by Zelthy</strong></p><p><br>\n</p><p>• India\'s largest oncology PAP currently managed by a Big Pharma (market cap ; 100Bn) end to end on Zelthy including patient onboarding to product tracking </p><p>• All HIV positive patients in India monitored by the Government through a program implemented on Zelthy (more than 1 million patients) </p><p>• South East Asia\'s leading healthcare company with presence in more than 12 countries has adopted Zelthy as their core technology backbone for running patient programs </p><p>• India\'s largest ePharmacy has adopted Zelthy as the core technology powering their patient program CRMs </p><p>• India\'s first controlled distribution network for a pharmaceutical product in India implemented launched by an Indian Big Pharma on Zelthy</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Founders</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Anshuman Chaudhary, CEO, Zelthy (B.Tech, IIT Delhi | Ex-PwC)</p><p>Kaustubh Chandrabhan, CTO, Zelthy (B.Tech, IIT Delhi | Ex-Avendus)</p>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Bengaluru, Karnataka, India', 'Zelthy', 'Shraddha Agrawal', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244564734/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=X1j70uFsGT7TtENPLweFEw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Zelthy Cloud enables quick and secure deployment of healthcare applications. Our proprietary framework enables minimum development time and cost while ensuring that applications adhere to healthcare compliances and data security requirements.', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244564734/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=X1j70uFsGT7TtENPLweFEw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:21:36'),
(26, 'Laravel Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p>The ideal candidate is a highly resourceful and innovative developer with extensive experience in the layout, design and coding of websites specifically in PHP format. You must also possess a strong knowledge of web application development using PHP programming language, MySQL Server databases and Laravel Framework.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform a mix of maintenance, enhancements, and new development as required</li><li>Develop, record and maintain cutting edge web-based PHP applications on portal plus premium service platforms</li><li>Work in a data analyst role and with business intelligence applications</li><li>Develop, record and maintain cutting edge web-based PHP applications on portal plus premium service platforms</li><li>Ensure HTML, CSS, and shared JavaScript is valid and consistent across applications</li><li>Utilize backend data services and contribute to increase existing data services API</li><li>Work cross-functionally to convert business needs into technical specifications</li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>3+ years\' of experience in web development and software design</li><li>Expertise in front-end technologies (HTML, JavaScript, CSS), PHP Laravel frameworks, and MySQL databases</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India', 'The Intellify®', 'HR - The Intellify', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245050094/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=kiMPA%2BTkr7hOZcYvZj0nyQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'About-The Intellify\n\nThe Intellify is a Top Rated AR and VR Development Company, HeadQuartered in India with offices in USA and UAE too. Founded in 2018, with around 50 team members offering Feature-Rich and Business Specific applications that are meticulously thought, designed and developed using the Top Trending Technologies, Augmented Reality and Virtual Reality.\n\nIntellify’s in-house services and expertise includes, Augmented and Virtual Reality Solutions, AR Filters, 3D Modelings and Animations and WebAR. We highly and accurately serve industries like Ecommerce, Digital Media, Manufacturing and Production Units, Educational Sectors, Healthcare Sectors, Gaming Industries and many more such.\n\nOur experts have in-depth knowledge of their respective domain and believe in fostering the development of captivating applications and solutions. We tend to build a bridge between the Brands/Business with Customers, giving them an Immersive Realistic Experience to their needs of Products and Services with the creation of Augmented Reality and Virtual Reality applications.\n\nOur team are coded with experience in technological branches like Unity 3D, Vuforia, ARKit, ARCore, Wikitude, HTML5, Angular JS, JavaScript, Laravel, etc. Also we have a creative approach for entrancing experience creation on Maya, 3D Max, PhotoShop, Blender, Zbrush, DeepAR, SparkAR, Snap Lenses, etc.\n\nVision and Mission:\n\nOur objective is to stay Determined and Focused in exploring more possibilities in the wide frame of AR and VR development, addressing Client’s desired requirement to bring in their Services and Solutions in best Realistic experience with the help of Augmented and Virtual Reality.\n\nWe strongly believe in Creating a New World of Experience for Client’s and their End Customers. Sharing the commitment to cater your Business with ‘Creative and Immersive AR and VR Solutions’, to sustain and succeed in the Longer Run.\n\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245050094/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=kiMPA%2BTkr7hOZcYvZj0nyQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:21:41'),
(27, 'Php laravel developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember79\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                Position Vacant: 3 [1 Senior(2-3 yrs experience) and 2 Junior (upto 1year)]<br>\n<br>\nJob Location: Ahmedabad<br>\n<br>\nExperience: 1 to 3 years<br>\n<br>\nQualification:Graduate (Preferable BE/ BTech/ ME/ MTech/ MCA/ BCA/ MSc)<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Job Description<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>We are looking for a motivated PHP / Laravel developer to come join our agile team of professionals.<br>\n<br>\nIf you are passionate about technology, constantly seeking to learn and improve skillset,then you<br>\n<br>\nare the type of person we are looking for!<br>\n<br>\nWe are offering superb career growth opportunities, great compensation and benefits.<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Responsibilities<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Develop,record and maintain cutting edge web-based PHP applications on portal plus<br>\n</li></ul>premium service platforms<br>\n<ul><li>Build innovative,state-of-the-art applications and collaborate with the User Experience (UX)<br>\n</li></ul>team<br>\n<ul><li>Ensure HTML, CSS, and shared JavaScript is valid and consistent across applications</li><li>Prepare and maintain all applications utilizing standard development tools</li><li>Utilize backend data services and contribute to increase existing data services API</li><li>Lead the entire web application development life cycle rightfrom conceptstage to delivery<br>\n</li></ul>and post launch support<br>\n<ul><li>Convey effectively with all task progress, evaluations,suggestions,schedules along with<br>\n</li></ul>technical and process issues<br>\n<ul><li>Documentthe development process, architecture, and standard components</li><li>Coordinate with co-developers and keeps project manager well informed of the status of<br>\n</li></ul>development effort and serves asliaison between developmentstaff and project manager<br>\n<ul><li>Keep abreast of new trends and best practices in web development<br>\n</li></ul><strong><u>Skills<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Strong knowledge of PHP web frameworks(such as Laravel, Yii, etc depending on your<br>\n</li></ul>technology stack)<br>\n<ul><li>Understanding the fully synchronous behavior of PHP</li><li>Understanding of MVC design patterns</li><li>Basic understanding of front-end technologies,such as JavaScript, HTML5, and CSS3</li><li>Knowledge of object oriented PHP programming</li><li>Understanding accessibility and security compliance (Depending on the specific project)</li><li>Strong knowledge of the common PHP or web server exploits and theirsolutions<br>\n</li></ul>Understanding fundamental design principles behind a scalable application<br>\n<ul><li>User authentication and authorization between multiple systems,servers, and environments</li><li>Integration of multiple data sources and databasesinto one system</li><li>Familiarity with limitations of PHP as a platform and its workarounds</li><li>Creating database schemasthatrepresent and support business processes</li><li>Familiarity with SQL/NoSQL databases and their declarative query languages</li><li>Proficient understanding of code versioning tools,such as Git<br>\n</li></ul>Skills:- MySQL, Laravel and CodeIgniter\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India', 'Genius Placement Service', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245049634/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=DvCfl0CWFSE%2B85CDsDrQGA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Genius Placement Service is a consumer services company based out of 13/155parishram Appartment 132 Ft. Ring Road, Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India.', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245049634/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=DvCfl0CWFSE%2B85CDsDrQGA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:21:49'),
(28, 'Software Engineer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember81\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                <strong>Greetings From PETPOOJA !!!<br>\n<br>\n</strong><strong><u>At The Outset, Your Candidature Is Found Suitable For An Opening Please Find Hereunder The Details Of The Requirement For Your Consideration<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong><strong> Designation:</strong> Software Engineer<br>\n<br>\n<strong> Location:</strong> Ahmedabad- Gujarat<br>\n<br>\n<strong>Company Website: </strong>http://www.petpooja.com ( Please go through the web link )<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Responsibilities<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Work with development teams and product managers to create software solutions.</li><li> Design client-side and server-side architecture. </li><li>Build the front-end of applications. </li><li>Develop and manage well-functioning databases and applications. </li><li>Write effective APIs. </li><li>Test software to ensure responsiveness and efficiency.</li><li> Troubleshoot, debug and upgrade software. </li><li>Create security and data protection settings. </li><li>Build features and applications with a mobile responsive design. </li><li>Write technical documentation.</li><li>Work with data scientists and analysts to improve the software.<br>\n</li></ul><strong><u>Qualifications<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>Degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering or relevant field.<br>\n<br>\nExperience with Java, Spring, and Restful API\'s.<br>\n<br>\nExperience with Database development (MySQL, Postgres, etc).<br>\n<br>\nProven experience as a Full Stack Developer or similar role. Knowledge of multiple front-end languages and libraries (e.g. HTML/ CSS, JavaScript, jQuery).<br>\n<br>\nKnowledge of multiple back-end languages (e.g. Java, Python) and JavaScript frameworks (e.g. Angular, React, Node.js).<br>\n<br>\nFamiliarity with databases (e.g. MySQL, MongoDB), web servers (e.g. Apache), and UI/UX design.<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Experience With AWS Or Other Cloud Environments<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>Skills:- MySQL, Laravel, CodeIgniter, Yii, MongoDB, PHP, CakePHP, HTML/CSS, NodeJS (Node.js), React.js, Javascript, Fullstack Developer, MERN Stack and MVC Framework\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India', 'Petpooja', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245046511/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=SCHOOL_RECRUIT&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=NiHfoL69zkJnNsv4P4WLXg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Established in the Year 2011, Petpooja is the largest next-generation PoS platform for the F&B sector with more than 45,000+ clients across India, UAE and South Africa\n\nWe are present in more than 140 cities across India and UAE, with more than 750+ employees working on a mission to organize the unorganized restaurant sector in India and globally with the help of technology.\n\nThe company is funded by High-Profile Investors (Fund of Funds). Founders of Petpooja have 20+ years of combined experience in Technology, Supply Chain Operations, Finance/Venture Capital and Customer relationship roles.\n\nPetpooja platform handles more than 2,00,000 invoices daily with more than 50,00,000 API calls per day. The platform is OS (Windows, Mac, Linux) independent and Browser independent. The platform encompasses technologies like – Node.JS, Python, PHP, Adobe, MySql, MongoDB, SqlLight, and ReactJS.\n\nWe work closely with companies/organizations like Zomato, Dunzo, Swiggy, IIFL, HDFC Bank, PayTM, NPCI, etc. The platform is at fore-front (in the world) in building and applying next-generation Machine Learning Models to Personalized Recommendation Engine using Data from PoS.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245046511/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=SCHOOL_RECRUIT&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=NiHfoL69zkJnNsv4P4WLXg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:21:54');
