(35, 'Web Developer / Full Stack Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember71\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                The internet continues to develop at great speed, and ProProfs remains on the cutting edge with their delightfully smart tools for smarter employees &amp; happier customers. Were looking for a skilled web developer to join our innovative team who are consistently raising the bar on creativity and delightful experiences. The ideal team member will develop smart solutions for the product and integrations to handshake with various 3rd party services.<br>\n<br>\nThe web developer will have an immediate effect on our brand and promises, as well as an ongoing impact in solidifying our industry-wide reputation for product experience.<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Requirements<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Strong problem solving and analytical skills. This is the key requirement.</li><li>Programming knowledge in Core PHP with clear understanding of OOPS based development.</li><li>Strong development experience with any PHP framework like Symfony, Laravel, CodeIgniter, etc.</li><li>Good problem solving experience using JavaScriptorES6with earlier versions.</li><li>Should have hands-on working experience with MySQL, writing efficient SQL queries, implementing joins, etc.</li></ul>\n            <br>\n            <h3 class=\"js-skills-header t-16 t-black--light t-bold\">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n            C,C++,Java,JavaScript,PHP,Angular,CodeIgniter,jQuery,Laravel,React.js\n        </span>\n      ', 'Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India', 'ProProfs', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3241615762/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=HLjw3EK9r5vpMh6R9T4ieg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'ProProfs\' Delightfully Smart Tools are used by millions of users each month. The site hosts more than one million pieces of content in 70+ languages and is a leading platform for online training and assessment with the world\'s largest library of professional tests & quizzes.\n\nProProfs products include -\n\n- Survey Maker\n- Live Chat\n- Help Desk\n- Knowledge Base\n- Project Management\n- Training Maker\n- Learning Management System\n- Polls\n- Quizzes\n\nProProfs Smart tools used by many Fortune 500 companies such as Sony, Accenture, Cisco & Dell, along with users from leading educational institutes like Phoenix, Harvard & Yale.\n\nMillions trust our delightfully smart tools.\n+10 Million Learners\n+10 Million Quiz Takers\n+100,000 Quizzes and Tests\n+1 Million Flashcards\n+100,000 Brain Games\n\nProProfs was founded by Sameer Bhatia on the vision that knowledge should be freely available to people from all walks of life.\n\nProProfs empowers users with a valuable platform to apply knowledge, helping them increase productivity, efficiency, and profitability.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3241615762/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&tr