(36, 'Full Stack Engineer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p>Urgent Hiring for full stack web developer (PHP)</p><p>Experience upto 2 years </p><p>Location -Vaishali (Ghaziabad)</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Job Description</p><p>Technical Skills: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap, jQuery ,PHP (Laravel/Codeignitor), Python(django), React js, Node js ,Web Service/ Web API, Firebase Database: MysQL</p><p>Requirements : -</p><p>1. Should be able to complete projects in full - Front end and Back end</p><p>2. Good understanding of HTML, Js query, CSS &amp; Ajax</p><p>3. Should able to design and develop the website as per the latest trends</p><p>4. Should have experience in integrating payment gateways</p><p>5. Should be able to deploy the website on main server</p><p>6. Strong PHP programming skills and Development experience for PHP, Custom development</p><p>7. Good database skills – Sql, MysQL</p><p>8. Understanding of latest Google algorithms</p><p>Responsibilities: - 1. Design and develop the website as per the requirements</p><p>2. Designing the user interface and web layout using advanced front end languages </p><p>3. Making the APl\'s or databases for the applications</p><p>4.Building backend and Frontend with CMS or Custom code</p><p>5. Integration of backend data</p><p>6. Design, develop and test the application as per the specifications </p><p>7. Submit daily work Report to the reporting manager</p>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India', 'Gendigi Technologies', 'Kamal Verma', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246586465/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=hTPyFKW%2B8jVOByJAFOmGIA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Gendigi Technologies is one of the leading Website Design and Development, Mobile App Development, e-commerce Shopping Site