(43, 'PHP Intern', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p><strong>Job Brief:</strong></p><p>The Brihaspati Infotech (P) Ltd. is hiring <strong>PHP Intern</strong> who loves to work with an amazing team and is passionate to learn new technologies.</p><p><strong>Location: Phase 8b, Mohali, India (Local Candidates)</strong></p><p><strong>Experience: Minimum 3 - 6 months of internship / industrial training in PHP is mandatory.</strong></p><p><strong>JOB SUMMARY: - Good knowledge in PHP, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap.</strong></p><p><strong>Salary:</strong> <strong>10-12k (Depends upon interview)</strong></p><p><strong>Education: Any B-tech(CSE), BCA, MCA, M-tech(CSE), B.SC(IT), M.SC(IT), Diploma Holder.</strong></p><p><strong>Notice Period: Immediate Joiner.</strong></p><p><br>\n</p><p>Company Highlights:</p><p>Medical Insurance.</p><p>Employee recognition and appreciation every month.</p><p>Employee engagement activities like monthly Fun Activity, Badminton Tournament, Cricket Tournament, Table Tennis along with Festival Celebrations</p><p>Salary on time.</p><p>Employee Hold: 150+</p><p><strong>Job Types: Full-time, Fresher, Permanent</strong></p>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Sahibzada Ajit Singh Nagar, Punjab, India', 'The Brihaspati Infotech Pvt. Ltd.', 'Vertika Sharma', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244540431/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=fPiM8p4fFS8UpVySMcX3cg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'The Brihaspati Infotech Pvt. Ltd. is a global digital service provider acclaimed for Design, Development, Marketing & Consultation of Web and Mobile based applications.\n\nFounded in 2010, we have emerged as trusted working partners around the globe. We facilitate Startups, Enterprises and Agencies with innovative technologies to outperform the competitive environment. With our unparalleled experience, complete communication and diverse capabilities, we have built a reputation of a reliable service provider.\n\nWe implement Agile best practices to offer offshore and onshore solutions for Web & Mobile application development with User Interface designing, Digital marketing, Server management and other IT services.\n\nOur Expertise includes:\n• CMS & Frameworks - WordPress, WooCommerce, Drupal, Shopify, BigCcommerce, Magento, Joomla, Opencart, Yii, CakePHP, Codeigniter, Zend, Ionic, React Native.\n\n• Coding Languages – Php Html5, Css3, JavaScript, jQuery, Ajax, Json, XML, REST and SOAP API services, Bootstrap, Java, Objective-C, Swift, Angular.js, Node.js, React.js, MySQL, MongoDB, Firebase.\n\n• Web Marketing - On & Off page SEO, Social Media integration, Email Campaigns, Analytics, Video Campaigns.\n\n• Web & Graphic Designing - Adobe Photoshop & Adobe Illustrator, SKETCH.\n\nWe set up effective digital business strategy to Create, Collaborate, Deploy and Deliver quality solutions to all our global business communities.\nClient satisfaction is our satisfaction and this is the hallmark of our success. We have been working round the clock with global clients to turn them into high-performance corporations.\n\nWe believe in respecting our clients, understanding their needs and living up to their expectations. By maintaining high standard of ethics in our work values, we deliver great business and optimized services required by the clients.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244540431/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=fPiM8p4fFS8UpVySMcX3cg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:24:02'),
(44, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember72\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                <strong><u>Job Description<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Framework: CodeIgniter is mandatory, Laravel will be an advantage.</li><li>Hands-on experience of OOPS, PHP, MVC frameworks, MySQL, CSS, AJAX, HTML5, CSS3.</li><li>Should be able to work under tight deadlines.</li><li>Expert in JavaScript, JQuery, Ajax.</li><li>Solid understanding of how web applications work including security, session management, and best development practices.</li><li>Excellent Debugging, Optimization skills, analytical, and problem-solving skills.</li><li>Working Experience in SOAP and RESTful APIs.</li><li>Working Experience in Git.</li><li>Must have the capacity to work independently and also as a part of a team.</li><li>Ability to learn new technologies.</li><li>Good Communication Skills.<br>\n</li></ul><strong><u>Roles &amp; Responsibilities<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>The developer is expected to be able to perform all aspects of the development tasks, including front-end, back-end, and database development.</li><li>Develop web applications and rich multimedia experiences according to the brief and technical specifications.</li><li>Must have experience and knowledge in CodeIgniter Framework.</li><li>The applicant is expected to possess strong problem-solving skills, programming, testing, and troubleshooting skills.</li><li>Must have knowledge of web services and serialization techniques like REST, SOAP, XML &amp; JSON.</li><li>Proficiency in PHP, jQuery, JavaScript, CSS, HTML, MySQL.</li><li>Should have a very strong knowledge of Core PHP.</li><li>Eagerness to contribute to a team-oriented environment.</li><li>Job Type: Permanent, Full-time, Work From Office</li><li>Experience: 1 year to 5 years</li></ul> Skills:- MySQL, Laravel, CodeIgniter, Javascript, jQuery, JSON, AJAX, Git and JWT\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India', 'Softonauts Infotech Pvt Ltd', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245049452/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=iF37vp1ugePM%2F1vSRhnCRw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Our services are process driven as capably as agile ample to acquiesce going on to client budgets and times guidelines. Our clientele consists of companies represented by choice industry verticals in India.', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245049452/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=iF37vp1ugePM%2F1vSRhnCRw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:24:11'),
(45, 'Fullstack Developer (Node+ Angular)', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember69\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                Job Role: Full Stack Developer<br>\n<br>\nProfile Summary<br>\n<br>\nWe are looking for a dynamic Full Stack Software Developer who is hard-working, analytical, takes on challenges and is excited by the idea of owning the development of a new platform. You will support end to end design, development, implementation, and integration of a web-based platform we are creating to help us best serve our customers.<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Responsibilities<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Need a person who takes ownership and fast enough to grab the requirements</li><li>Write modular code that can be effectively used in future development work</li><li>Maintenance, bug fixes and enhancements for existing apps</li><li>Consult with internal teams to define technical requirements, capabilities and guide architectural decisions</li><li>Clear and consistent communication with management and project stakeholders<br>\n</li></ul><strong><u>Requirements<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Client-side development in HTML5, CSS3 and JavaScript object-oriented, typescript object-oriented</li><li>Back-end development in Node.js</li><li>Good experience on MongoDB.</li><li>Front end development in Angular.</li><li>Should have experience in Node.JS API, Jason, node.js connector and node.js batch operations.</li><li>Good with MySQL.</li><li>Knowledge of Oracle and\\or SQL Server is a priority.</li><li>Knowledge of best practices in web development</li><li>Willingness to continually learn new technologies</li><li>Open to code reviews and pair programming</li><li>Ability to handle changing priorities, manage multiple tasks and work within tight deadlines</li><li>Desire to take complete ownership of assigned projects</li><li>Strong communication skills</li><li>MySQL</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Itanagar, Arunachal Pradesh, India', 'ISHIR', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246280122/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=1dcKCiTitC2jIajIYOhcbQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'ISHIR is a globally diversified leading offshore software development company with experience and expertise in a broad range of services and solutions. With 20+ years of experience in the IT industry, ISHIR enables cost-effective and dependable software outsourcing solutions. We have over 900 satisfied clients across the globe in different industries.\n\nWe are experts in the field of software development, web design and development, managed cloud services, software testing, application development services and custom software development.\n\nHeadquartered in Dallas, with global delivery center in Noida, India, we are one of the preferred software development companies with a unique combination of skilled people, world-class processes and robust technology. To learn more, visit www.ishir.com\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246280122/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=1dcKCiTitC2jIajIYOhcbQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:24:20'),
(46, 'Senior Systems Analyst', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <strong>Lionbridge Technologies</strong> is a provider of translation, development and testing solutions. Lionbridge combines global resources with proven program management methodologies to serve as an outsource partner throughout a client\'s product and content lifecycle - from development to translation, testing and maintenance. Global organizations rely on Lionbridge services to increase international market share, speed adoption of global products and content, and enhance their return on enterprise applications and IT system investments.<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Position Description<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>Lionbridge is seeking a talented individual to lead a group of software developer and QA engineers. He should be a full stack developer, comfortable reviewing code, making architectural decisions. Unit testing and refactoring is the norm in your day to day development activities. Educating and mentoring less skilled team members should come naturally.<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Responsibilities<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li> Understand high level business requirements and produce technical specifications, designs, architecture input, and ultimately code</li><li> Develop accurate time-estimates for work assignments and oversee those provided by other developers on your team</li><li> Development of production quality code and the design and development of unit tests.</li><li> Participate in product requirement and design reviews</li><li> Work independently with other Developers, Product Managers and an Architectural Lead</li><li> Ensure highest level of technical quality, security, scalability, interoperability and stability in all products that are developed</li><li> Investigate, analyse and document reported defects</li><li> Respond to user support requests and issues<br>\n</li></ul><strong><u>Required Skills And Experiences<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li> 10+ years of experience developing full stack web-based software using .NET including, C# and relevant web standards such as JavaScript, CSS and JQuery is required</li><li> Expertise in: .Net, C#, Web API 2, Angular JS, JavaScript, and upwards with Visual Studio</li><li> Experience with frontend technologies: CSS/HTML/JavaScript, popular frontend frameworks (such as Angular, React, etc.)</li><li> Experience with leading development team</li><li> Experience in MVC, will be good</li><li> Experience with CI/CD</li><li> Knowledge of Cassendra, Rabit MQ</li><li> Experienced working on the Azure Platform</li><li> Knowledge of Kubernetes / Docker, Azure Service Fabric, Azure DevOps</li><li> Ability to analyze business requirements, working closely with business analysts to drive out the details of requirements</li><li> Ability to produce maintainable, scalable, developer tested solutions, to contribute to and adhere to development standards and good practice</li><li> Expertise in problem solving and debugging complex systems</li><li> Patient, flexible attitude, ability to perform under pressure</li><li> A commitment to quality and a thorough approach to the work</li><li> Ability to work well within a team or alone</li><li> Good verbal and written English communication skills<br>\n</li></ul><strong>Education<br>\n</strong><ul><li> Bachelor\'s degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering or a related area is preferred.</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Mumbai, Maharashtra, India', 'Lionbridge', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246290342/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=Z2qzmuKlgScAJB1jGgj%2FnQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Lionbridge partners with brands to break barriers and build bridges all over the world. For 25 years, we have helped companies connect with their global customers and employees by delivering translation and localization solutions in 350+ languages. Through our world-class platform, we orchestrate a network of passionate experts across the globe who partner with brands to create culturally rich experiences. Relentless in our love of linguistics, we use the best of human and machine intelligence to forge understanding that resonates with our customers’ customers. Based in Waltham, Massachusetts, Lionbridge maintains solution centers in 23 countries. Learn more at www.lionbridge.com.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246290342/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=Z2qzmuKlgScAJB1jGgj%2FnQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:24:28'),
(47, 'Python Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p><strong>Job Title</strong> <strong>:</strong> Python Developer </p><p><strong>Department</strong> <strong>: </strong>Etech Technology Solutions (ETS) </p><p><strong>Location : </strong>Gandhinagar, Gujarat </p><p> </p><p>Our team is growing – but we are not adding members just to fulfill requests. We are searching for individuals who are ready to be a part of the next big thing and are excited about growing with our company! Leadership is anxiously waiting to cultivate and develop your skills and prepare you for the career journey of a lifetime. </p><p>Our focus is to create lasting impressions with each customer interaction. Reflect on the times you have been the customer and you left your experience feeling satisfied, appreciated, and valued. Simply put – these are the experiences you will use to deliver world-class results to our customer base. </p><p> If you consider yourself to be a team player, goal-oriented, and possess a passion for helping others; apply to become a part of the Etech Global Services Team. </p><p> </p><p><strong>ABOUT US:</strong> </p><p>Globally, we are over 3000 strong, and we are always searching for new team members which will offer fresh and innovative ideas and diverse approaches to everyday problem-solving. Etech is governed by 12-character commitments: Integrity, Valuing People, Teamwork, Accountability, Communication, Vision, Adaptability, Humility, Creativity, Teachability, Positive Influence, and Courage. Together, these 12 commitments guide our workplace culture and set the tone for how we treat each other. </p><p> </p><p>Visit us: <strong><u>www.etechgs.com</u></strong></p><p> </p><p> <strong>WHAT WE OFFER:</strong> </p><ul><li>Transportation allowance </li><li>Canteen Subsidy </li><li>Night Shift allowance as per the process </li><li>Schedule Attendance Bonus </li><li>Health Insurance </li><li>Tuition Reimbursement </li><li>Incentive components campaign wise. </li><li>Work-Life Balance Initiatives </li><li>Rewards &amp; Recognition </li><li>Internal movement through IJP </li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Skills &amp; Experience</strong></p><ul><li>Must have 3+ years of expert-level understanding python libraries OS, re, pandas, requests, Django, Flask, data mining, parsing, cleaning, transforming, web scraping, NLP etc.</li><li>Experience in development of web solutions using Django/Flask.</li><li>Experience in React.Js added advantage.</li><li>Exposure RDMS or NO-SQL database added advantage.</li><li>Knowledge of Elastic Search, SQL query, different API method and security implementation for PCI/HIPPA compliance.</li><li>Solid python background and familiar with data types and databases, and experience with different libraries to implement production solution.</li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Gather the requirements for different projects of business analysis and develop python scripts for data cleaning and transformation.</li><li>Automate data ingestion process in different speech to text analytics platforms.</li><li>Develop python script to connect with different data sources and extract information required for business analytics.</li><li>Web site development using Django/Flask.</li><li>Knowledge of web-scraping, APIs method calls.</li><li>Develop APIs to deliver data to different application integration.</li></ul><p></p>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Gujarat, India', 'Etech Global Services', 'Sweta Soni', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245016854/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=ySsuk0PW2k21d%2FAcs1kwfQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Etech Global Services is a servant leader organization committed to making a remarkable difference for each other, our customers, and within our communities. Etech offers a suite of services that includes inbound and outbound customer care, quality monitoring and analytics, email, live chat, technical support, back office support, and software development. Our current partnerships with more than 47 companies include managing upwards of 100 million voice interactions, 20 million chat and email interactions, and 2 million quality monitoring evaluations per year.\n\nEtech launched in 2003 with only 400 employees and a single contact center in Nacogdoches, Texas. Over the last 17 years, we have expanded our range of services and have grown to include more than 3,000 employees and eight state-of-the-art contact centers with five U.S., one nearshore, and two offshore locations. All of this has been accomplished without the need for mergers or acquisitions.\n\nEtech’s company partnerships have benefited from our proven track record of creating improved customer experiences, enhanced customer satisfaction and advocacy, increased conversion rates, higher net promoter scores, and stronger customer relationships.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245016854/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=pHM0x9%2B28zXmeI68XstrUA%3D%3D&trackingId=ySsuk0PW2k21d%2FAcs1kwfQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:24:38'),
