otivated, self-starter with a goal-oriented personality.</li><li>Team player.</li><li>Experienced carrying a high workload in a high-pressure, fast-paced work environment and relentlessly focused on impact.</li><li>Excellent written and verbal skills.<br>\n</li></ul><strong><u>Compensation And Requirements<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Salary will vary based on skill level and experience.</li><li>Restricted stock options are available after 1 year.</li><li>Time off as needed.</li><li>Confidentiality and invention assignment agreement required.</li></ul>\n            <br>\n            <h3 class=\"js-skills-header t-16 t-black--light t-bold\">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n            Java,JavaScript,PHP,Python,Angular,Node.js,React.js,Vue.js\n        </span>\n      ', 'Bengaluru, Karnataka, India', 'Authenticate™', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3241618579/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=rQ%2F3YOwRGfXQI8JhBA%2Bfow%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Authenticate™ provides developer tools for identity authentication and fraud prevention by integrating multiple verification tools so customers can create proprietary trust scores on peer-to-peer exchanges, two-sided marketplaces, online communities and others worldwide through the Authenticate.com API and mobile SDK.\n\n• Low-cost AML, KYC, FCRA, DPPA, EEOC and FHA compliant checks are available through channel partnerships with leading CRAs and data furnishers.\n\n• Our unified solution saves our customers time to market, R&D and the cost of managing multiple integrations and accounts.\n\n• The combined purchasing power of our customers, preferential pricing and a direct line of contact to upper management results in lower costs and a higher level of support than our customers would receive by going direct to our partners.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3241618579/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=rQ%2F3YOwRGfXQI8JhBA%2Bfow%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:26:14'),
(55, 'Full Stack Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember82\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                <strong>Warm Greetings</strong><p><br>\n</p><strong> We are currently Looking for Full Stack Developer</strong><p><br>\n</p><ul><li> Mandatory Skills Required :Full stack Developer(react.js/angular.js And Node.js) </li><li> Knowledge of Typescript and Loopback.io would be an added advantage </li><li> RelevantExperience : minimum 2 is mandatory and maximum 5 years </li><li> Location : Remote </li><li> Notice Period : Immediate joiner or Maximum 30 days if Serving Notice Period </li><li> If you are interested, let me know. References also Welcome. </li></ul><p><br>\n</p><strong> Contact Number : 9150028158</strong><p><br>\n</p><strong> E mail : anitha@aicc.biz</strong><p><br>\n</p>This job is provided by Shine.com\n            <br>\n            <h3 class=\"js-skills-header t-16 t-black--light t-bold\">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n            frontend, backend, react.js, node.js, angular.js, \"full stack developer\"\n        </span>\n      ', 'Belgaum, Karnataka, India', 'Axon International Coaching and Consulting', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245006893/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=i3BadHZcM%2BTtCvdf%2F4LyqA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'AICC is a startup initiative for coaching and consulting firm that believes in the power of the human capital. We believe that everyone has the capability to do wonders and achieve excellence they only need the right direction and guidance. We at AICC are always ready to nurture people and help them grow. The investment in human and intellectual capital is the best investment that is bound to deliver returns irrespective of the market conditions.\n\nAICC was started in 2021 with a vision to provide solutions to all areas of human resource development under one roof to our clients. It is a task to have separate consultants for various areas like Life Coaching , Business Coaching, Career Development and Sales Training, Staffing, SEO, Content Writing, Skill Development, Recruitment, Training\'s, Management Advisory, Employee Satisfaction Surveys, etc.\n\nWe serves both large and small organizations across all industry sectors through our brands and offerings: Coaching and Talent solutions.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245006893/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=i3BadHZcM%2BTtCvdf%2F4LyqA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:26:19'),
(56, 'Web Development Internship in Pune at OneDot Enterprises Private Limited', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember82\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                <strong><u>About OneDot Enterprises Private Limited</u></strong><p><br>\n</p>OneDot Enterprises Private Limited is a privately held IT services company from Pune, Maharashtra. We provide various services including machine learning, artificial intelligence, data analytics, web design &amp; development, Android &amp; iOS development, e-commerce development, digital marketing, etc. We\'ve been working on many kinds of projects adding to our wide exposure amount. With the wide integration of technology in each of our products and services and constant innovation in our thought processes, we aim to deliver better values.<p><br>\n</p>Activity on Internshala<p><br>\n</p>Hiring since May 2020<p><br>\n</p>32 opportunities posted<p><br>\n</p>4 candidates hired<p><br>\n</p><strong><u>About The Internship</u></strong><p><br>\n</p>Selected intern\'s day-to-day responsibilities include:<p><br>\n</p><ul><li> Create web application layout/interface by using standard practices</li><li> Integrate data from back-end services and databases</li><li> Write well designed, testable and efficient code from scratch</li><li> Work on web based applications e.g. ERP, Website, etc</li><li> Work on End-To-End development and solution</li></ul><p><br>\n</p>Skill(s) required<p><br>\n</p>Bootstrap CSS HTML JavaScript jQuery MySQL PHP ReactJS<p><br>\n</p>Learn these skills on Internshala Trainings<p><br>\n</p>Learn PHP<p><br>\n</p>Learn MySQL<p><br>\n</p>Specialize in Full Stack Development<p><br>\n</p>Learn HTML<p><br>\n</p>Learn CSS<p><br>\n</p>Learn Node.JS using Javascript<p><br>\n</p>Learn Software Testing using Javascript<p><br>\n</p>Learn Bootstrap<p><br>\n</p>Learn ReactJS<p><br>\n</p>Who can apply<p><br>\n</p><strong><u>Only Those Candidates Can Apply Who</u></strong><p><br>\n</p><ul><li> are available for full time (in-office) internship</li><li> can start the internship between 29th Aug\'22 and 3rd Oct\'22</li><li> are available for duration of 3 months</li><li> are from or open to relocate to Pune and neighboring cities</li><li> have relevant skills and interests</li><li> Women wanting to start/restart their career can also apply.</li></ul><p><br>\n</p>Perks<p><br>\n</p>Certificate Letter of recommendation Flexible work hours Job offer<p><br>\n</p>Additional Information<p><br>\n</p>Job offer: On successful conversion to a permanent employee, the candidate can expect a salary of Rs. 5 to 9 Lac/annum<p><br>\n</p>Number of openings<p><br>\n</p>1<p><br>\n</p><strong><u>Additional Questions</u></strong><p><br>\n</p><strong>Sign up to continue</strong><p><br>\n</p>Sign Up with Google<p><br>\n</p>OR<p><br>\n</p>Email<p><br>\n</p>Password<p><br>\n</p>First Name<p><br>\n</p>Last Name<p><br>\n</p>By signing up, you agree to our Terms and Conditions .<p><br>\n</p>Already registered? Login<p><br>\n</p><strong>Sign up to continue</strong><p><br>\n</p>Sign Up with Google<p><br>\n</p>OR<p><br>\n</p>Email<p><br>\n</p>Password<p><br>\n</p>First Name<p><br>\n</p>Last Name<p><br>\n</p>By signing up, you agree to our Terms and Conditions .<p><br>\n</p>Already registered? Login\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Pune, Maharashtra, India', 'OneDot Enterprises Private Limited', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245058756/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=obAmxJO%2FXmC7%2FJYWxxPfGQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'We are a private limited company working in various sectors. We got incorporated in May 2020. Currently our services include Political Consulting, Information Technology and Event Management. In coming years, we are aimed to enter into various product and services based industries as well. We believe in \'no boundaries\' thought processes and aspirations.\n\nFounded by Mr Rajjab Nadaf, and co-founded by Mr Suyog Purohit and Mr Soheb Shaikh, all being school friends who have their expertise in different work areas, had a belief of working together with the idea of empowering passion and professions.\n\nRajjab Nadaf, a computer engineer by profession, always ached about creating employment for the young and talented candidates from rural area like Jath, Maharashtra. It was always been in his mind that \'students from rural area are talented but they lack in resources and platforms to present their talent.\' In order to achieve this, OneDot Enterprises helped him successfully step towars his desire to fill up the gap between rural and urban areas in terms of market aspects.\n\nOneDot Enterprises Private Limited\'s wide range of services include\n🔖 ML & AI\n🔖 Data Analytics\n🔖 Web Design\n🔖Web Development\n🔖 E-commerce Development\n🔖 Android and iOS Development\n🔖 Digital Marketing\n🔖 Payment Gateway\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245058756/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=obAmxJO%2FXmC7%2FJYWxxPfGQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:26:24');
