(64, 'Laravel Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p><strong>Description</strong></p><p>Hand on and Expert Developer - PHP with Laravel</p><p>We are looking for champion developers. The job entails hands-on coding so we are not looking for managers or team leads.</p><p>We assure you that you would get cutting-edge projects to work on with us.</p><p>Expert level developer with 2 years of experience in Database, Admin UI, Middleware, and API</p><p>&gt; Must-Have</p><p>Demonstrated experience on Server frameworks (more than one is desirable) Laravel (mandatory)</p><p>UI development knowledge based on Bootstrap (mandatory)</p><p>Strong knowledge of HTML, CSS, JQUERY, and AJAX</p><p>API Development (mandatory)</p><p>Rest API with the ability to create documentation</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>building and maintaining modern web applications using standard web development tools.</p><p>writing clean and secure modular codes that have undergone strict testing and evaluation.</p><p>checking the validity and consistency of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript on different platforms.</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><p>Previous working experience as a PHP / Laravel developer for 2 year(s)</p><p>BS/MS degree in Computer Science, Engineering, MIS or similar relevant field.</p><ul><li>In-depth knowledge of object-oriented PHP and Laravel 8 PHP Framework.</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Maharashtra, India', 'Kleverowl Solutions Pvt Ltd', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245004566/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=JaT4X6MG5n5B39hsO5AChw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245004566/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=JaT4X6MG5n5B39hsO5AChw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jo