(65, 'Java Application Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p>Currently we are hiring as Sr Java developer.</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Job Location: Banjara Hills_ Hyderabad</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong><i>Role: Sr Java developer (WFO)_ Monday-Friday</i></strong></p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p><strong>Full Stack Java Developer(Server Side Development, Front end HTML wiring-up using JQuery, Bootstrap, Build and Deploy)</strong></p><p><strong>Should ensure and implement coding standards and should be responsible for the technical aspects of the project delivery.</strong></p><p><strong>Administer the application</strong></p><p><strong>Create new screens</strong></p><p><strong>Modify the process flow</strong></p><p><strong>Adding/using the existing additional fields in the system to accommodate new data elements</strong></p><p><strong>Placing the additional fields on screens and implement the new screens versions</strong></p><p><strong>Hands-on Native MySQL query is must.</strong></p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Key Technical Skills</strong>:</p><p>Programming Languages - <strong>Java 7</strong></p><p><strong>Frameworks - Spring MVC, Struts 2.0</strong></p><p><strong>Database - MySQL</strong></p><p><strong>Scripting - Jquery, Javascript, jsp</strong></p><p><strong>Servers - Tomcat</strong></p><p><strong>Configuration management - SVN</strong></p><p><strong>IDE - Eclipse</strong></p>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Hyderabad, Telangana, India', 'MaxData Solutions', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3239994809/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=%2Fcx45eUR2gjdUK7GCpjNAQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'MaxData has been set up to provide cost effective, efficient & quality oriented software solutions, analytics and data to the community. The company is made up of experienced p