(68, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                Hi My name is Osama <br>\nI am an HR in Appcake and Looking for a Backend Developer for a Work From Home opportunity. Let me know if you are comfortable with that then I can schedule your interview. <br>\n<br>\n➡️Position: Back end<br>\n🏢Company: AppCake<br>\n💻Format: remote work<br>\n💰Conditions: RFP (depends on experience, we are ready to discuss your wishes)<br>\n<br>\n🧁AppCake is an innovative product company that has specialized in successful mobile app development since 2017. We conquer the IT industry with a non-trivial approach, interesting tasks and the active use of modern technologies. The released products are distinguished by positive download growth, intuitive interface and easy perception by end users. Our goal is to create quality products that are understandable and easy to use. Our customers are millions of users of applications based on Android and iOS.<br>\nWorking in AppCake is a creative process in a team of professionals. The company provides an opportunity for each employee to build a successful career by implementing bold ideas and using their full potential.<br>\n<br>\nRequirements:<br>\n- 4+ years of experience in web development (PHP 7+ / JS / MySQL / Symfony 4+ / Rabbit MQ / Docker / Redis and other frameworks);<br>\n- Good understanding of OOP principles and their use in practice;<br>\n- Experience in building CRM systems is a plus;<br>\n- Experience with CRM systems would be a plus<br>\n- Knowledge and experience with Node.js will be a plus.<br>\nMain goals:<br>\n- Writing servers and services for the needs of the company, ranging from APIs for mobile applications to parsers and CRM systems.<br>\n<br>\nWhat are the tasks and projects?<br>\nVarious, you can find out more at work, this information is under the NDA (and here, if anything, you can include everything that will relate to tasks, projects)<br>\n<br>\nHow many people are on the team?<br>\nThere are up to 10 people in the backend developer team (there is a separate frontend team), that is, you will only need to deal with backend development and only sometimes fullstack.<br>\n<br>\nWhat\'s the stack? - (PHP 7+ / JS / MySQL / Symfony 4+ / Rabbit MQ / Docker / Redis and other frameworks)<br>\n<br>\n🔗Our website: https://appcake.info/ I’m #hiring. Know anyone who might be interested?\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'India', 'AppCake', 'Osama Dilshad', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245056257/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=Czy%2BRUhCVIbtxWvlpLSubw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'AppCake - An innovative product company that has been specializing in the successful development of mobile applications since 2017. We conquer the IT industry with a non-trivial approach, interesting tasks and the active use of modern technologies.\n\nThe released products are distinguished by positive download growth, intuitive interface and easy perception by end users. Our goal is to create quality products that are understandable and easy to use. Our customers are millions of users of applications based on Android and iOS.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245056257/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=SPTNjbtlvetbeKwqNv60bQ%3D%3D&trackingId=Czy%2BRUhCVIbtxWvlpLSubw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:28:14'),
(69, 'Laravel Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember79\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                <strong><u>Requirements<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Two to three years of experience in development in PHP (CorePHP, Laravel, CodeIgniter) and MySQL, Mongodb in an n-tier architecture.</li><li>Basic understanding in designing(HTML, Bootstrap, CSS, JavaScript, AJAX, jQuery).</li><li>Strong background in object-oriented development techniques, best coding practices, and security concepts.</li><li>Experience in developing reports using common third-party APIs and Plugins.</li><li>Should have very good communication skills and strong analytical skills.</li><li>Experience with concurrent development source control (Git).</li><li>Deploy project on server.</li></ul>\n            <br>\n            <h3 class=\"js-skills-header t-16 t-black--light t-bold\">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n            PHP,CodeIgniter,Laravel\n        </span>\n      ', 'Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India', 'Sagenext Infotech LLC', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https:/