d Conditions .<p><br>\n</p>Already registered? Login\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Jaipur, Rajasthan, India', 'Helpful Insight Private Limited', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245055745/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=a0%2FTrLuBCWPin4TsjewwBA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Helpful Insight Pvt Ltd is one of the well-known leaders in the technology revolution and provides complete IT solutions since 2015. The company has successfully established itself as a leading company in the Development world within a short period.\n\nOur Expertise\nThe company provides the best services in Mobile application, Website development, Designing & Digital marketing. We are a team of highly professional experts.\n\nWe have a team of accomplished web developers, UX/UI designers, and app developers who operate for clients from across the world.\n\nThrough our offshore development, we can provide a service that is truly unique to others in the industry, at affordable and competitive rates.\n\nIf you have a vision that you want to make a reality get in contact with our experts Today !!\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245055745/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=a0%2FTrLuBCWPin4TsjewwBA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:30:04'),
(74, 'Application Front end Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                HIR ING<br>\n<br>\nJob Skills<br>\n<br>\nReactJS - UI, Web Development Technique, User Interface<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Description<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>Hi<br>\n<br>\nHigh High Demand 100 - REACT JS , HTML, CSS<br>\n<ul><li> Total IT Experience – 7 to 11 years</li><li> 7+ years of front-end UI development experience in REACT JS</li><li> 3+ years of experience in HTML/CSS/Bootstrap</li><li> 3+ years in React.js/Redux development covering Responsive web site development, creating self/contained, reusable and testable modules and components</li><li> 3+ years of experience in Java script, Jquery</li><li> 2+ years of experience in Node JS is a nice to have</li><li> 1+ year of REST API Integration with web pages to Persist (Add/Update/Delete) the screen data into database to Display the data to the User</li><li> Familiar with Continuous Integration methodologies and tools, including Jenkins</li><li> Familiar with testing frameworks (Ex. Jasmine) and test runner framework (Ex. Karma)<br>\n</li></ul><strong>Skill<br>\n<br>\n</strong><strong><u>Years Of Experience<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong><strong>Skill type (Mandatory/Good to Have)<br>\n<br>\n</strong>HTML 5/CSS 3/Bootstrap<br>\n<br>\n3+<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Primary<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>React.js/Redux/Saga Pattern, ZEST Framework<br>\n<br>\n3+<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Primary<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>Java script, jQuery<br>\n<br>\n3+<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Primary<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>Node JS<br>\n<br>\n2+<br>\n<br>\nSecondary<br>\n<br>\nREST API Integration<br>\n<br>\n1+\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Mumbai Metropolitan Region', 'Hexaware Technologies', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245004092/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=%2F3S8DYIl76NKwh5ZuUXduw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Hexaware is an automation-led next-generation service provider delivering excellence in IT, BPS and Consulting services. We are driven by a combination of robust strategies, passionate teams and a global culture rooted in innovation and automation. Hexaware’s digital offerings have helped clients achieve operational excellence and customer delight. Our focus lies on taking a leadership position in helping clients attain customer intimacy as their competitive advantage. We are on a journey of metamorphosing the experiences of the customer’s customers by leveraging our industry-leading delivery and execution model, built around the strategy— ‘Automate Everything®, Cloudify Everything®, Transform Customer Experiences®’. Powering Hexaware’s complex technology solutions and services is the Bottom-Up Disruption, a disruptive crowdsourcing initiative that brings about innovation and improvement to everyday complexities and, ultimately, growing the clients’ business. The digitally empowered, diverse and inclusive workforce of Hexaware represents various nationalities, comprising 24,166 employees, and thoroughly lives the company’s philosophy of ‘customer success, first and always’.\n\nExciting, isn’t it? Follow Hexaware to get a glimpse of technology disruptions and exciting digital transformations on the horizon. To learn more, visit www.hexaware.com\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245004092/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=%2F3S8DYIl76NKwh5ZuUXduw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:30:13'),
(75, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                Develop, record, and maintain cutting-edge web-based PHP applications on portal plus premium service platforms<br>\nBuild innovative, state-of-the-art applications and collaborate with the User Experience (UX) team<br>\nEnsure HTML, CSS, and shared JavaScript is valid and consistent across applications<br>\nPrepare and maintain all applications utilizing standard development tools<br>\nUtilize backend data services and contribute to increase existing data services API<br>\nLead the entire web application development life cycle right from concept stage to delivery and post launch support<br>\nConvey effectively with all task progress, evaluations, suggestions, schedules along with technical and process issues<br>\nDocument the development process, architecture, and standard components<br>\nCoordinate with co-developers and keeps project manager well informed of the status of development effort and serves as liaison between development staff and project manager<br>\nKeep abreast of new trends and best practices in web development<br>\nPrevious working experience as a PHP / Laravel developer for (x) year(s)<br>\nBS/MS degree in Computer Science, Engineering, MIS or similar relevant field<br>\nIn depth knowledge of object-oriented PHP and Laravel 5 PHP Framework<br>\nHands on experience with SQL schema design, SOLID principles, REST API design <br>\nSoftware testing (PHPUnit, PHPSpec, Behat)<br>\nMySQL profiling and query optimization<br>\nCreative and efficient problem solver\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'New Delhi, Delhi, India', 'SoftiCation Technology', 'Amarnath Rana', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244573749/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=%2FmkWYe%2FnOgqZ7ffyKjWb2w%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'SoftiCation Technology is a professional web & Mobile App design & development company in India. We are specializing in E-Commerce, Mobile App, Software, Web Application, Website design, and development, Content Management System, Online CRM, Digital Marketing, Application Development, Information Management, Custom Software Development, Mobile Application Development, Software Testing, Cloud Application Development& Cloud Consulting for customers all over the world.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244573749/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=%2FmkWYe%2FnOgqZ7ffyKjWb2w%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:30:22'),
(76, 'Front End Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember73\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                We are currently looking for Front - End Developer with 2+ years of work experience with good communication and strong technical skills.<p><br>\n</p><strong> <u> Designation:</u> </strong> Software Engineer and Senior Software Engineer<p><br>\n</p><strong><u>Requirement</u></strong><p><br>\n</p><strong> <u> Job Description:</u> </strong><p><br>\n</p>Strong understanding of JavaScript, its quirks, and workarounds<p><br>\n</p>Strong understanding of features and utility functions of jQuery / JS Frameworks (Vue JS), React<p><br>\n</p>Strong understanding of web mark-up, including HTML5 and CSS3<p><br>\n</p>Good understanding of browser rendering behavior and performance<p><br>\n</p>Understanding of asynchronous request handling, partial page updates, and AJAX.<p><br>\n</p>Familiarity with input validation techniques and approaches<p><br>\n</p>Working experience in dynamic website or portal and API integration<p><br>\n</p><strong><u>Role And Responsibilities</u></strong><p><br>\n</p>Ensure the technical feasibility of UI/UX designs<p><br>\n</p>Optimize components for maximum speed and scalability<p><br>\n</p>Ability to roll out well-implemented custom java script plugins or modules<p><br>\n</p>Ability to implement data manipulation / data binding from Rest APIs.<p><br>\n</p><strong><u>Qualification</u></strong><p><br>\n</p>BE/B.TECH/MCA background<p><br>\n</p><ul><li> Experiences 2+ Years</li><li> Good communication skills</li><li> Immediate joiners only or the candidate who can join within 15 to 20 days </li></ul><p><br>\n</p>This job is provided by Shine.com\n            <br>\n            <h3 class=\"js-skills-header t-16 t-black--light t-bold\">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n            bootstrap, end, html5, javascript, front, developer, css\n        </span>\n      ', 'Bengaluru, Karnataka, India', 'INFINITI RESEARCH MARKETING SOLUTIONS INDIA PRIVATE LIMITED', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245001783/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=4ei%2FAn8Kx%2Fk7ABR0LEvsow%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'INFINITI RESEARCH MARKETING SOLUTIONS INDIA PRIVATE LIMITED is a transportation/trucking/railroad company based out of \"\"EMBASSY SIGNET\"\" SURVEY No.13/1 KADUBEESANAHALLI, VARTHUR HOBLI, BANGALORE, Karnataka, India.', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245001783/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=4ei%2FAn8Kx%2Fk7ABR0LEvsow%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:30:30');
