(77, 'PHP Developer- (2-4 yrs)', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <strong>Role <br>\n<br>\n</strong>PHP Developer<br>\n<br>\n<strong>Location<br>\n<br>\n</strong>Noida<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Experience<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>2-4 year<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Skills<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>PHP, MySQL, PHP programming, REST API, JavaScript and jQuery, Stored Procedures<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Responsibilities<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Hands-on 2-3 years of programming experience in PHP-MySQL</li><li>Knowledge of object-oriented PHP programming</li><li>Experience in integration of REST API</li><li>Excellent in JavaScript and jQuery</li><li>Good Knowledge in JSON, XML, HTML5 and CSS3</li><li>Hands-on experience in MYSQL database in writing DDLs, DMLs, Stored Procedures, Views, Functions and Indexing</li><li>Strong analytical and problem-solving skills</li><li>Understanding the fully synchronous behavior of PHP</li><li>Understanding of MVC design patterns</li><li>Basic understanding of front-end technologies, such as JavaScript, HTML5, and CSS3<br>\n</li></ul><strong><u>Who We Are<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong><strong>About the company: <br>\n<br>\n</strong>The pursuitâ€¦<br>\n<br>\nA checkered flag. A scenic panorama unfolding around the bend. A trophy catch. A pulse-quickening stretch of road or trail. Heads turning as you pass by. Even coming home at the end of a hard day\'s work.<br>\n<br>\nWhatever your pursuit, It is there, too, pursuing our goals. We want to satisfy our customers and exceed their expectations with products and services of superior quality, unmatched performance, and extraordinary value.<br>\n<br>\nWith an ever-expanding line that includes motorcycles, outboard motors, ATVs, personal watercraft, snowmobiles, boats, outdoor power equipment, race kart engines, accessories, apparel, and much more, we at Yamaha Motor Corporation, U.S.A., strive to contribute to the quality of life. Your life.<br>\n<br>\nLife can have many exciting, memorable experiences. Creating opportunities for them is what it is all about.<br>\n<br>\n<strong><u>Why Should You Have To Apply<br>\n<br>\n</u></strong>We know that with the right people on board, anything is possible.<br>\n<br>\nThe quality, integrity, and commitment of employees are key factors in this company\'s growth, market presence,<br>\n<br>\nand ability to help their clients stay a step ahead of the competition.<br>\n<br>\nBy hiring the best people and helping them grow both professionally and personally, they ensure a bright future.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>For more details contact sankarasundari.m@cielhr.com</strong>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India', 'CIEL HR', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244339920/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=d48yGGVo5bzv4SZrVd8iVA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'CielHR marks the return of HR visionaries to the HR Services industry, powered by technology and analytics. The Founders of Ma Foi, the pioneer of the HR services sector in India, along with some of the finest brains in the HR Services Industry have envisioned and built the firm, CielHR, to deliver the full range of Recruiting services from Executive Search, Recruitment Process Outsourcing and Staffing Permanent as well as Temporary roles through its offices in India and Middle East.\n\nCiel is a French word meaning sky. For us, it’s the peak of excellence that we strive to achieve as we fulfill your talent needs and meet career aspirations of candidates.\n\nAdvanced data sciences and analytics have been applied by the in-house technology team to build a unique IT system for CielHR that helps us find the most suitable candidates in the shortest possible time.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244339920/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=d48yGGVo5bzv4SZrVd8iVA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:30:39'),
(78, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Conducting analysis of website and application requirements.</li><li>Writing back-end code and building efficient PHP modules.</li><li>Developing back-end portals with an optimised database.</li><li>Troubleshooting application and code issues.</li><li>Integrating data storage solutions.</li><li>Responding to integration requests from front-end developers.</li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in computer science or a similar field.</li><li>Knowledge of PHP web frameworks including Yii, Laravel, and CodeIgniter.</li><li>Knowledge of front-end technologies including CSS3, JavaScript, HTML5,</li><li>jQuery and Bootstrap.</li><li>Understanding of object-oriented PHP programming.</li><li>Proficient with code versioning tools including Git, Mercurial, CVS, and SVN.</li><li>Familiarity with SQL/NoSQL databases.</li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Perks &amp; Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Flexible Working Hours</li><li>ESOP - Employee Stock Option Plan</li><li>20-70% Hike on Salary</li><li>Young and Enthusiastic Team</li><li>5 Days working</li><li>Friendly work Environment</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Rajkot, Gujarat, India', 'TilesWale', 'Kinnari Trivedi', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3241344854/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=D1T6ld3IY6gerxPQO7A9pQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Your home solution, Our Unique Way! Tileswale is a name you can count on when it comes to all your housing solutions. Tileswale meets all of your requirements, whether you\'re looking for stylish kitchen and bath ware, or commercial ceramic solutions.\n\nOur foundation is built on the highest-quality products and the best customer service, and we have hundreds of retail locations throughout India. We offer an unmatched sales experience. Being one of the finest tile companies in India is a result of the fact that we have maintained a strong commitment to our core values of innovation, product quality, and customer focus since the beginning.\nWe have a substantial audience in many different nations because to our extensive selection of tiles, bathware, and flooring options, which has allowed us to grow our customer base internationally.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3241344854/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=D1T6ld3IY6gerxPQO7A9pQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:30:47'),
(79, 'Wordpress Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember69\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                <strong><u>Responsibilities<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>Design, implement and manage websites using WordPress</li><li>Collaborate with members of a creative team</li><li>Manage front-end and back-end website development</li><li>Create WordPress plug-ins and themes is a plus</li><li>Maintain well-documented, reusable, and transferrable code</li><li>Troubleshoot and resolve website problems for clients and co-workers</li><li>Stay abreast of new developments in software, trends, and practices<br>\n</li></ul><strong><u>Requirements<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li>This position requires an associate or bachelor\'s degree, preferably in computer programming, computer science, or a related field.</li><li>Employers look for job candidates with extensive WordPress experience.</li><li>Skills and CompetenciesSkills and Competencies</li><li>Proficiency using WordPress</li><li>Expertise in HTML5 CSS3 JavaScript, and jQuery</li><li>Experience usin