(80, 'Full Stack Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                Job Description<br>\n<br>\nOpenings Full-Stack Developer<br>\n<br>\nAre you motivated in learning new technologies in the fields of Web Application development and want to work with team members from Canada? Join us and develop the most challenging products of your lifel You will work with experienced web developers in our tools and technologies.<br>\n<br>\nResponsibilities<br>\n<br>\n• Write clean and functional code across the stack.<br>\n<br>\nExperience working in an Agile/Scrum environment. • Manage dato integrations with third party data services.<br>\n<br>\nAngularJS or React presentation framework experience. Responsible for following the team\'s established Agile processes which<br>\n<br>\ninclude supporting both short and long-term planning, cross-functional support, and demonstrating working software. • Experience with programming and software development.<br>\n<br>\nJob Type: Full-time Remote<br>\n<br>\nQualifications<br>\n<br>\nProven working experience in web design and programming, at least 1 year Experience working with HTML, CSS, JavaScript,<br>\n<br>\nBootstrap, Python React<br>\n<br>\nExperience in Node.JS, AngularJS and React is definitely an asset.<br>\n<br>\nPython Django is definitely an asset<br>\n<br>\nObject-Oriented design principles are required • Proven effective communication in English\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India', 'CEFAS Technologies', 'Ratan Narayan Pratap', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244378929/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=9gbqv9B%2FKfmG0LbMC28GEg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Cefas Tech has a team of young and passionate entrepreneurs who have rich expertise in the design & development of websites and ap