(81, 'Python Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p><strong>We have an opening for Python Developer</strong></p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Makarba, Ahmedabad</p><p><strong>Experience: </strong>3-5 yrs</p><p><strong>Salary:</strong> Upto 8 LPA</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p><p> </p><ul><li>2-3 years of commercial work experience of <strong>Python/Django</strong></li><li>Strong knowledge of web environments, <strong>API designs, HTTP, REST, WebSockets</strong></li><li>Valid experience in designing and implementing low-latency, high-availability, and performative applications</li><li>Experience with common Python frameworks and libraries (<strong>Django and Django Rest Framework(DRF)</strong> is required)</li><li>Must required hands on experience with <strong>either Ubuntu Or Linux </strong></li><li>Good knowledge of relational and non-relational databases</li><li>Contribute towards every stage of the software development life cycle like designing solutions, writing code, testing code, automating tests and deployment.</li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p><strong> </strong></p><p><strong>Nice to have:</strong></p><p><strong>﻿</strong></p><ul><li>Experience of Server-less development with <strong>AWS Lambda</strong> or other similar solutions</li><li>AWS services: <strong>ECS, SNS, S3, RDS</strong></li><li>Knowledge of <strong>JavaScript </strong></li><li>Knowledge of <strong>AngularJS framework</strong></li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India', 'HRemedies', 'Simran Mahto', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244593943/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=QtGPP7qemTuU9kNoReEUlg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'HR-Remedies was founded with a mission to help organizations accomplish