(82, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <strong><u>Job Description<br>\n</u></strong><ul><li> Should have rich experience in PHP, and MySQL.</li><li> Demonstrated skills in creating web applications, services, and APIs.</li><li> Finalizing back-end features and testing web applications.</li><li> Write clean, well-designed code.</li><li> Experience with PHP Frameworks such as Laravel (Preferred)or Symfony(Preferred).</li><li> Contribute to all phases of the development lifecycle.</li><li> Experience with version control systems GIT.</li><li> Experience debugging across multiple web browsers.</li><li> Thorough knowledge of relational database design and development,MySQL.</li><li> Integrations like REST and SOAP experience is a strong plus.</li><li> Basic Understanding of Frontend technologies such as JavaScript, HTML5,and CSS3.<br>\n</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', 'Cynosure Corporate Solutions', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3241391105/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=jwj8TsYS%2FEdyldYUWl8kng%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Cynosure Corporate Solutions is a human capital services company. cynosure\'s focus is to provide Executive Search, Recruitment, Training, Temporary Staffing services, Statutory Compliances, and other HR aligned services. Cynosure understands the business goals of our clients and their need to align human resources to these goals.\n\nCynosure is committed to provide high quality manpower in accordance to global standards and their requirements. Cynosure candidates stand testimony to our professional competency. One of the major tools in the process is our comprehensive databank, which is updated regularly.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3241391105/?eBP=