(95, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p>Job location: Noida (on-site)</p><p>Desired Experience: 1 - 5 years (Experience in Laravel is must)</p><p>Salary: Negotiable</p><p>Course Specialization: B.E/ B.Tech/ B.C.A</p><p>Tentative date of joining : Immediate</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Job description</p><p>- Coding in PHP, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery; MySQL, WordPress</p><p>- Assist in Project architecture, maintenance &amp; upgradation</p><p>- Troubleshooting web application; UI/UX design, AWS Server Handling</p><p>- GIT repository management &amp; deployment</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Required Candidate profile</p><p>- Knowledge of PHP, HTML, JavaScript, CSS, Bootstrap, MySQL.</p><p>- Knowledge in server hosting like c panel, AWS, GIT.</p><p>- SEO</p><p>- Troubleshooting web application</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Location: - Address: A-94/9, Bishanpura Rd, Shital Vihar, A Block, Sector 58, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301</p><ul><li>Interview Mode: - Face to Face</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India', 'Careerera -SNVA EduTech', 'Shazman Qureshi', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245039722/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=PjeTtZ4riG1ChAe8Ti2fIg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Careerera was founded in 2014 by founder Mr Vivek Kumar Singh and Mr Alok Kumar Singh.\nCareerera is an online education provider company of professional certification training, based in Herndon, Virginia, USA. Careerera is regarded as one of the front-runners in offering qualitative online courses to the ones who really wish to go ahead in their career by earning quality certifications. All the certification courses provided by us are in complete sync with the liking and requirements of the students. The courses offered by us are highly beneficial for the students who are running out of time and can’t spare time for doing any courses. As all the courses are rendered to you online so everybody can do these courses. The students who choose us for getting certification programs can get benefit of our online classes and grow in their career. We are completely aware of the importance of the time of our students so we proffer them the best tutorial through our learned guides and faculty members. Students who go for our course can use our video tutorials, interactive glossary, crossword, phone app, chapter tests, sample papers and so on. Some of the courses provided by Careerera are as follows:-\n\n· Red Hat System training\n· Scrum master certification\n· Android course\n· Java Certification\n· PMP programs\n· ITIL courses\n· Comptia A+\n· Nursing assistance certification\n· PMI courses\n· Prince2 training\n· Big Data Hadoop Training\n· Professional medical auditor course\n· Comptia network+\n. Six Sigma\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245039722/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=PjeTtZ4riG1ChAe8Ti2fIg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:33:18'),
(96, 'HTML Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <p>Role: Sr. Front-end developer</p><p>Experience: Min 3 years</p><p>Location:</p><ul><li>1st Floor S- 2 Ivory Palms IT Park Road, Gayatri Nagar, Nagpur - 440022</li><li>Raj Palace, Square, behind Bank of India, New Mankapur, Nagpur, 440030</li></ul><p>Package: Min 4 LPA (Final package will depend upon the interview performance)</p><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Required Skills </strong></p><p><br>\n</p><p>● HTML, CSS, Bootstrap and Javascript- 3+ years of experience is a must.</p><p>● Hands-on knowledge of WordPress.</p><p>● Knowledge of WordPress Template tags is a must.</p><p>● Should be able to apply Bootstrap concepts effectively.</p><p>● Good communication skills.</p><p>● Experience building scalable front-end websites in WordPress.</p><p>● Demonstrated leadership in an engineering environment in driving best practices.</p><p>● Able to deal with ambiguity. Strive for clarity in requirements and problem space to mitigate UI risks upfront.</p><p>● Make the appropriate trade-offs to balance innovative UX with implementation complexity.</p><p>● Evaluate the risks and benefits of using front-end libraries, frameworks, and tool sets for a given problem.</p><p><br>\n</p>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Greater Nagpur Area', 'VowelWeb', 'Huzefa Kapadia', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246714816/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=fulVCdhS3VnH01xl8v%2BvYQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Started by a visionary in 2013, Vowel Web is a Product Base Company situated in Nagpur, India. We are proud and happy to tell you the fact that we have proved us as one of the rapidly growing companies in Nagpur satisfying our clients globally. We are having an experienced team who have their hand expertise in Programming and Marketing. We move forward with the aim of becoming the most results oriented Web Development Company in India.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246714816/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=%2F0Nl5lxp%2Bfb5x8Ha%2BiPcxQ%3D%3D&trackingId=fulVCdhS3VnH01xl8v%2BvYQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:33:27'),
(97, 'Frontend Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <ul><li>Designing and developing user interfaces using angularJS best practices.</li><li>Adapting interface for modern internet applications using the latest front-end technologies.</li><li>Writing JavaScript, CSS, and HTML.</li><li>Developing product analysis tasks.</li><li>Making complex technical and design decisions for AngularJS projects.</li><li>Developing application codes and unit tests in AngularJS, Java Technologies, and Rest Web Services.</li><li>Conducting performance tests.</li><li>Consulting with the design team.</li><li>Ensuring high performance of applications and providing support.</li></ul><p><br>\n</p><p><strong>Ideal Candidate</strong></p><p><br>\n</p><ul><li>BTech, BSc., MSc., BTech or PhD in Computer Science or in related areas</li><li>Very good command of English</li><li>Minimum 5 years of experience in developing web-services and applications for diverse industries</li><li>Experience in designing and developing responsive UI applications and backend applications for web and mobile platforms</li><li>Proven skills and experience in following latest cloud-based application development technologies:</li><li>Typescript, Angular 9, HTML5, CSS</li><li>MindShere, Azure IoT, AWS IoT, IBM Watson</li><li>Hands-on experience in designing and developing software applications for web/cloud and IoT platforms (Mindsphere, AWS, Google Cloud, Microsoft Azure or IBM Bluemix etc.)</li><li>Experience in git is must and knowledge in Azure devops is a plus.</li><li>Experience with Junit and Mockito, Jasmine and Karma is a big plus.</li><li>Passionate for developing simple, clean, and attractive code</li><li>Strong problem solving and analytical skills</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Pune, Maharashtra, India', 'Capgemini', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246920483/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=WYq%2BMAVQATx0JM4DyapmRg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Capgemini is a global leader in partnering with companies to transform and manage their business by harnessing the power of technology. The Group is guided everyday by its purpose of unleashing human energy through technology for an inclusive and sustainable future. It is a responsible and diverse organization of over 350,000 team members in more than 50 countries. With its strong 55-year heritage and deep industry expertise, Capgemini is trusted by its clients to address the entire breadth of their business needs, from strategy and design to operations, fueled by the fast evolving and innovative world of cloud, data, AI, connectivity, software, digital engineering and platforms. The Group reported in 2021 global revenues of €18 billion.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246920483/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=COMPANY_RECRUIT&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=WYq%2BMAVQATx0JM4DyapmRg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:34:22'),
(98, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember71\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                Exp: 0-3 years; PHP Developer No. Of Openings 10 Working Days (Monday Friday) Salary Package Best for deserving candidates Education Qualification B.Tech / BCA / MCA Key Responsibilities Candidate should have good knowledge of Core PHP and MySql database. Strong fundamentals in OOPS, MySQL, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Jquery. Knowledge and Experience in Developing Web Applications using any CMS like WordPress, Joomla, Magento, Drupal or WooCommerce. Knowledge / Experience of any one framework like Laravel, CodeIgniter, Cake PHP, Yii, Shopify etc. Good communication skills are desired.\n            <br>\n            <h3 class=\"js-skills-header t-16 t-black--light t-bold\">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n            fundamentals , css , laravel , phpdeveloper , wordpress , joomla , javascript , jquery , database , shopify , drupal , cake , oops , codeigniter , yii , php , mysql , html , magento\n        </span>\n      ', 'Punjab, India', 'Tech Prastish Software Solutions Pvt. LTd', 'Rashim Karwal', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245030257/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=6BrhkfGKdzThF%2FMRVd9lTA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'TPSS have a highly skilled team to envision a perfect picture for wide ranging fitness app development including website and yoga apps, gym apps since 2008.\n\nTech Prastish Software Solutions is a Digital Specialist with the proficiency in digital fitness and wellness solutions that power boosts the business prospects and enhancing their website & app visibility.\n\nWe have been constantly helping its clients transform their businesses by providing powerful and integrated IT solutions since 2008. In short stint of little less than 10 years, the company has developed a world wide spectrum of clients and services. Aligning our business objectives with clients’ requirements has made us evolve into a dependable brand for our clients located in 32 countries across the globe. The company has been engaged in developing business solutions for small medium and large scale industries dealing with all kind of products and services.\n\nThere are more than 2000 businesses all around the world powered by technological solutions developed by Tech Prastish. Unparalleled expertise of its professionals, investment in technologies and outstanding customer service makes it the most preferred IT company. Tech Prastish strives to be a leading IT company while delivering innovation, adding value and competitive advantage to its clients.\n\nTech Prastish employs experienced and knowledgeable full time employees working from six state of the art facilities located at Mohali in North India. Tech Prastish service portfolio includes customized Software Solutions, Software QA and Testing, Healthcare, Content Management and E-Commerce services.\n\nTo summarize, Tech Prastish\'s international perspective, operational strengths ( trained human resources, world class infrastructure, processes and monitoring systems) coupled with the experience of servicing international projects, add signiﬁcantly to the company\'s capabilities to qualify as “Software Development” vendor.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245030257/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=6BrhkfGKdzThF%2FMRVd9lTA%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:34:30'),
(99, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember87\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                Strong knowledge of any PHP web frameworks such as codeigniter, Laravel, Yii, etc<p><br>\n</p>Strong knowledge of Core PHP<p><br>\n</p>Understanding of MVC design patterns<p><br>\n</p>such as JavaScript/Jquery, HTML5, and CSS3<p><br>\n</p>Good knowledge of oops concept, Mysql<p><br>\n</p>Salary 4 Lac To 7 Lac P.A. Industry IT Software - Application Programming / Maintenance Work Experience 2 - 7 Years Qualification Other Bachelor Degree<p><br>\n</p>,<p><br>\n</p>This job is provided by Shine.com\n            <br>\n            <h3 class=\"js-skills-header t-16 t-black--light t-bold\">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n            yii, oops, mysql, it, javascript, php, software, maintenance, laravel, codeigniter, \" core php\", html5, jquery, \" application programming\", html, design, \" zend framework\"\n        </span>\n      ', 'New Delhi, Delhi, India', 'Capital Placement Services Gurgaon .', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245019994/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=R%2BpNuWtUuUa%2BDjguZFJuUQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Capital Placement Services Gurgaon is an emerging leader in Executive Search. Capital Placement Services Gurgaon is building a tradition of providing professional, personalized, high quality services, tailor made to suit your individual needs and requirements. We have experience in both IT and non-IT Sectors such as FMCG, Retail, Telecom, Manufacturing, HealthCare, Banking, Insurance, Financial Services, and Research among others. Our forte is in identifying talent for Senior Management positions as well as Middle Management levels.\n\nWe undertake placements for both Domestic and International clients, and have ongoing engagements with several large MNC\'s within India and abroad. We operate through domain-specialist teams spread across the country, providing high quality permanent staffing services .Our success is our ability to connect the right people to the best Companies.\n\nWe are a well established and professionally managed Manpower Placement Consultants specializing in placement of managerial personnel across a wide spectrum of skills and functions. We have been in the industry for a decade and have been providing quality service to our clients across various industries. Our role begins with the client\'s need and we go to great lengths to understand the nature and complexity of the client\'s business. It is this power that helps us to provide our clients with candidates who are of the right profile.\n\n\nWe have huge data bank of candidates in all fields at all levels.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245019994/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=R%2BpNuWtUuUa%2BDjguZFJuUQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:34:39'),
(100, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold \">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n            <div id=\"ember73\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback artdeco-inline-feedback--note ember-view mb5\" role=\"status\">    <li-icon aria-hidden=\"true\" type=\"notify-pebble-icon\" class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__icon\" size=\"small\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" data-supported-dps=\"16x16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"mercado-match\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" focusable=\"false\">\n  <path d=\"M12 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-3 8v2H7.5A1.5 1.5 0 016 10.5a1.56 1.56 0 01.1-.5l1.08-3h2.13l-1.09 3zm0-3.75A1.25 1.25 0 1110.25 5 1.25 1.25 0 019 6.25z\"></path>\n</svg></li-icon>\n\n  <span class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__message\">\n      This job is sourced from a job board.\n      <button class=\"artdeco-inline-feedback__linktext\" aria-label=\"Learn more\" type=\"button\">Learn more</button>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<!---->        <span>\n                Exp: 2-3 years; Technical Skills Should have experience in Laravel PHP 5.2/5.3 /5.4 SQL / My SQL 5. X (cluster configuration and My SQL optimization) JavaScript / j Query (UI) Core PHP HTML and CSS The skills you need to excel in this position include Strong Analytical Skill Team Handling Skill Ability to work in a team environment with the willingness to share skills &amp; systems knowledge, best practices, standards, etc., with other team members. Ability to work under minimum supervision and with self-organizing teams. Excellent troubleshooting and debugging skills. Solid organization, verbal / written communication &amp; presentation skills. Experience working on an Agile/Scrum team environment Strong analytical skills (macro and micro) and process orientation Strong sense of personal accountability for results\n            <br>\n            <h3 class=\"js-skills-header t-16 t-black--light t-bold\">Desired Skills and Experience</h3>\n            laravel , css , php developer , javascript , sql , written communication , php , debugging , html , technical skills\n        </span>\n      ', 'Pune, Maharashtra, India', 'Magneto IT Solutions', NULL, NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245059033/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=4yAOJz4kFlGFkXvdGA2N9Q%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Magneto is an award-winning eCommerce agency. Our core competencies lie in developing market-leading end-to-end B2C, B2B eCommerce solutions development, ERP, CRM integration & Digital Marketing. From creating strikingly beautiful web stores to innovative mobile applications, our team uses the agile methodology to develop industry-leading User Interfaces to deliver the perfect experience to the end-user.\n\nUsing our resource strength of 90+, we help our clients scale their eCommerce businesses by implementing ground-breaking Digital eCommerce solutions. We help our clients increase the efficiency of their in-house team by improving and streamlining their customer acquisition and retention practices.\n\nWe are closely working with eCommerce ventures since 2011 and have helped 200+ brands for building/improving their online ventures in the area of UI/ UX, Development, Launching, Revenue Enhancement, Marketing strategy, and much more and 90% of ventures are generating very good revenue.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3245059033/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=4yAOJz4kFlGFkXvdGA2N9Q%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:34:48'),
(101, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                Hello Everyone<br>\n<br>\nWe are hiring PHP Developer Fresher and Interns.<br>\nLocation :- Ahmadabad <br>\nExperience - 0 - 6 month<br>\nInterested candidate share their resume at hr@vihadigitalcommerce.com <br>\nReference are most welcome.<br>\n<br>\nRegards<br>\nNiru Solanki<br>\nHR Executive\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India', 'Viha Digital Commerce', 'Niru Solanki', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244523366/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=NpsyRl6KalE3wXk3ZlvMOw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Viha Digital Commerce is an eCommerce web development agency that has created its own identity in the IT sector. We offer eCommerce Store Design and Development services at an affordable price with advanced platforms like Magento, Shopify & Prestashop, rated as one of the leading eCommerce brandings over the world.\n\nWe take the pride to announce that recently, our Magento Developers from our team have passed Magento exams to become certified Magento developers & another great achievement is we also become Magento Community Partner.\n\nViha Digital Commerce is a full-service eCommerce & CMS Web Development Agency(Over 8+ years of excellence 1500+ projects) that provides value-added services at affordable rates.\n\neCommerce Web development\nMagento Development\nMagento Enterprise Cloud\nMagento Speed Optimization\nMagento SEO\nMagento Extensions Development/Customization\nMagento Hosting\nMagento Upgrade\nMagento Migration\nMagento Cloud\nShopify Development\nPrestaShop Development\nCMS WordPress Development\nHire Dedicated Developers Facility\n\n\nWe provide online marketing services including SEO(Search Engine Optimization)/PPC/SMM. Our client base is spread across multiple regions including Europe, USA, Australia, Canada & UK. We provide highly-demanded, performance-oriented e-commerce & cms development.\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244523366/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=ACTIVELY_HIRING_COMPANY&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=NpsyRl6KalE3wXk3ZlvMOw%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:34:57'),
(102, 'Laravel Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                I am looking for Laravel developer to assist with my projects.<br>\n<br>\n should have experience with:<br>\n- laravel 8+<br>\n- Vuejs<br>\n- tailwind &amp; bootstrap<br>\n- Git, composer, NPM<br>\n<br>\nshould be available atleast 6 hours per day.\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'India', 'Freelance', 'Kishan Nath', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244507535/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=qKoIxYriZNCLo4tWH7nLlg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3244507535/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=qKoIxYriZNCLo4tWH7nLlg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:35:06'),
(103, 'Full-Stack Developer PHP', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                <ul><li>You have a strong academic record. A CS degree is preferred, but not required with relevant experience.</li><li>At least 2 years experience in full stack web development, with a strong understanding of modern Javascript and PHP.</li><li>PHP framework CodeIgniter, HTML5 and CSS3.</li><li>You are comfortable working with MySQL databases.</li><li>You are comfortable reading code written in other languages such as Java, and using UNIX shell commands.</li><li>You have a strong working knowledge of Git.</li><li>You are comfortable interfacing directly with clients and are not intimidated or frustrated by working collaboratively with stakeholders.</li></ul>\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'New Delhi, Delhi, India', 'Jamy Interactive, Pvt Ltd', 'Fiza Bano', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246276432/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=a75skAGYpyBUlwwAP3ZHpQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3246276432/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=a75skAGYpyBUlwwAP3ZHpQ%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:35:15'),
(104, 'PHP Developer', '\n          <h2 class=\"mt5 t-20 t-bold mb4\">\n            About the job\n          </h2>\n\n<!---->\n<!---->        <span>\n                Strong programming and technical PHP OOPS<br>\nDemonstrable knowledge of database ( MYSQL)<br>\nShould have experience in PHP frameworks laravel, CodeIgniter<br>\nProficiency with front-end scripting including: HTML, DHTML, JavaScript, CSS, AJAX, JSON and front-end development including jQuery.<br>\nClear concept of HTML5, CSS3, Javascript/Jquery\n<!---->        </span>\n      ', 'Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India', 'Webiators Technologies PVT. LTD.', 'HR Vaishali Ahirwar', NULL, 'General', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3240602307/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=fdCrfJP%2FSCER%2Bn41qT%2B0%2Fg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 'Webiators Technologies was launched in 2017, We also offer low cost \"Express\" solutions and multiple financing options for Ecommerce business . Since our inception in 2017, we have worked on different domain areas and have builtup our expertise on all fronts of the industry and have delivered to the requirements of 15s of businesses and organizations around the globe. Our team excels at seamlessly combining exceptional graphic design, dynamic Web programming and powerful online marketing. Our clients include globally recognized brands and smaller businesses in almost every vertical industry.\n\nAs we grow, we have committed ourselves to the ideas that founded our success:\n\n* Big picture thinking\n* Personalized attention\n* Results-focused innovation\n* Exceeding client expectations\n* Competitive pricing\n\n', 'https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/3240602307/?eBP=JOB_SEARCH_ORGANIC&recommendedFlavor=JOB_SEEKER_QUALIFIED&refId=ciLeNLkV7mjK6sckxtLTPA%3D%3D&trackingId=fdCrfJP%2FSCER%2Bn41qT%2B0%2Fg%3D%3D&trk=flagship3_search_srp_jobs', 1, 0, 'naukri', '2022-08-31 20:35:39');

